Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾以为这就是你故事的起点\N{\r英文}I used to think this was the beginning of your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.10,中文,,0,0,0,,记忆这东西作风诡异\N{\r英文}Memory is a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.18,中文,,0,0,0,,总是让我琢磨不透\N{\r英文}It doen't work like I thought it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我们完全受制于时间\N{\r英文}We are so bound by time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.14,中文,,0,0,0,,要跟随它的节拍\N{\r英文}By its order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.83,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，回到妈妈身边吧\N{\r英文}It's okay. Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,到妈妈怀里来\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.66,中文,,0,0,0,,到妈妈怀里来\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,举起手来！\N{\r英文}Stick em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:37.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你就是这镇上的警长吗？\N{\r英文}You are the sheriff from here town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:41.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我有把挠痒枪，现在要来收拾你了\N{\r英文}My tickle guns, now I'm  gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:46.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你想让我去抓你？那你快点逃吧\N{\r英文}You want me to chase you? You better run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得故事中间的片段\N{\r英文}I remember moments in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\r英文}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我恨你！\N{\r英文}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.43,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是终点了\N{\r英文}And this was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.59,中文,,0,0,0,,回到妈妈身边\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.39,中文,,0,0,0,,回到妈妈身边好吗\N{\r英文}Please come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:01.40,中文,,0,0,0,,可现在，我有点不相信起点和终点了\N{\r英文}And now Im not so sure I believe in beginnings and endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.22,中文,,0,0,0,,一些和你人生并无交集的日子，却勾勒出你的故事\N{\r英文}There are days that define your story beyond your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.90,中文,,0,0,0,,就好像他们降临的那天\N{\r英文}Like the day they arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:22.93,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\r英文}Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.79,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么就你们几个？\N{\r英文}Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.06,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们上课吧\N{\r英文}Ok... Well let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我们谈下葡萄牙语\N{\r英文}Today, we're talking about Portuguese
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.86,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么它的发音和其他罗马语系有较大差别\N{\r英文}and why it sounds so different from the other Romance languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:45.36,中文,,0,0,0,,葡萄牙语发源于加利西亚王国\N{\r英文}The story of Portuguese begins in the Kingdom of Galicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:48.86,中文,,0,0,0,,中世纪时期\N{\r英文}In the Middle Ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:54.15,中文,,0,0,0,,语言被视为一种艺术表达方式\N{\r英文}when a language was seen as an expression of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你有什么新闻想分享吗？\N{\r英文}Any news you want to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.88,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，你能打开电视机，调到新闻频道吗？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks can turn you turn the TV to the news channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.76,中文,,0,0,0,,警察已经在周边区域设置了路障\N{\r英文}... But police have already set up blockage around the area
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.50,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你可以看到，我们已经是尽可能接近了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}As you can see, we got just about as close as we can...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.67,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可遗憾的是，蒙大拿现在已经完全封锁了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}but unfortunately, Montana right now, is on complete lock down.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.75,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}40分钟前，不明物体{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The object apparently touched down...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.58,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}确认着陆在94号州际公路北面{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}40 minutes ago, just north of I-94.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们正等候消息，看这是不是艘实验飞船，又或者...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We are waiting to hear if this is perhaps an experimental vessel or...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.77,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}等下...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Hold on...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:50.01,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我刚得知，还有更多的这类物体{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Im learning that more objects like this{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.61,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在全球范围内的最少8处地点着陆{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Have landed in as many as eight other locations around the world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.01,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}好，我们可以播？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Yes, can we?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.91,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是北海道某地{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}This is from a site in Hokkaido.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.81,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是此时此刻正在全球发生的事件{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}This is worldwide and is happening right now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.07,中文,,0,0,0,,下课\N{\r英文}Class is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.31,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}目前我们只请求大家的配合{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}But for now we’re simply asking for cooperation{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.77,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}等候官方对此物体进行评估{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}while authorities assess the object.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.22,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那你就是说它不是我们国家的？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You are saying its not ours?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.47,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- 你根本不知道它是否来自地球吧？  - 我们正在收集消息{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}- Do you even know if its from Earth?  - We’re still collecting information...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.26,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}和其他国家协作{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}coordinating with other countries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.75,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}不只是我们的后院里冒出这么个东西{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We are not the only ones to have one of these in our backyard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.46,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果这是某种寻求和平的第一类接触{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}If this is some sort of peaceful first contact,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.83,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}为什么要来12艘，一艘就够了吧{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}why send twelve? Why not just one?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道，老妈\N{\r英文}I do not know, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你看的新闻都一样\N{\r英文}I'm watching the same news as you're.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.41,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈啊，别听那个台胡扯\N{\r英文}Mom...mom, please don't bother with that channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.67,中文,,0,0,0,,那些人都是白痴，我提醒过你多少次了？\N{\r英文}How many times I have to tell you those people are idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我哪紧张了？\N{\r英文}Do I sound nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.06,中文,,0,0,0,,就是，所以嘛...\N{\r英文}Ok, exactly...so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我？你了解我的，我还不是老样子\N{\r英文}Yeah, me? You know me. I'm about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.02,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈，我没事\N{\r英文}Mom, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好，我会再打给你的，再见\N{\r英文}Ok, I'll call you later, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.85,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...着陆到现在有差不多8小时了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}...and at around eight hours after landing,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:41.13,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}仍旧没有任何"第一类接触"的迹象{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}there are still no signs of what might be called 'first contact.'{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.86,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}不明物体最少有457米高{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Now the objects are measured at least 1500ft tall...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.30,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}据报道，还有2艘不明物体进入俄罗斯领空{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}...Two more have reported to have penetrated Russian airspace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:52.66,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一艘在西伯利亚，另一艘在黑海沿岸{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}One in Siberia and the other on the coast of the Black Sea...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:56.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}矗立在海面上，目前总计有12艘不明物体降落在全球各地{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}...standing above the ocean. So far there are 12 unidentified objects spread across the globe...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.46,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}它们的降落地点并无明显关联{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}...there is no obvious logic to their locations{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.13,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}没有证据表明这些飞船是...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}And no evidence that the ships are even occ...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:06.43,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果它的确是某种飞船，也不能排除{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}...entertain the idea that if it is a kind of vessel,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}它是无人驾驶的可能{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}it may be unmanned.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}不管怎样，我们有应对此类事件的一套方案{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Regardless, we have a protocol for scenarios like this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.01,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}委内瑞拉现场{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.44,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在经历了不同寻常的周二后{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}After Tuesday's extraordinary events,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}总统今早宣布全国进入紧急状态{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}the President this morning, has declared a state of emergency{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:30.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}仅蒙大拿州，就有约五千国名警卫队进驻{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}With as many as 5,000 National Guard being deployed to the state of Montana, alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.52,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}边境关闭，航班停飞{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Borders are closed and flights have been grounded,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}上百万旅客滞留机场{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}stranding millions of travelers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.94,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}汽油，瓶装水和食物价格飙升{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}gas, water and food continues to escalate{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.05,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}联邦政府暂时解除了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}and federal authorities have temporarily lifted{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.35,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}对执法部门的加班禁令{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}the overtime limit on law enforcement.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.95,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}烟酒枪械管理署已暂停发放新的持枪许可{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The ATF has put a temporary ban on new gun licenses,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.82,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}迫使许多独立供应商{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}forcing many independent suppliers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.85,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}抢购各类武器装备{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}of hunting equipment and firearms{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.04,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}并把公众拒之门外{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}to close their doors to the public.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.78,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}48小时过去了，在12个UFO着陆点{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}48 hours later and no further development...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.30,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- 仍未有新的进展  - 才2天{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}- from the site of twelve UFOs.  - Two days.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}公众就已经指望我们能解答一切了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Already the public expects us to know all the answers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我是GT韦伯上校\N{\r英文}I'm Colonel G.T. Weber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没有正式见过面，不过2年前\N{\r英文}We havn't formally met, but two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你给情报部门做过波斯语翻译吧？\N{\r英文}You did some Farsi translation for the Intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那些叛军视频的翻译工作你干得很利索\N{\r英文}You made quick work of those insurgent videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟那些叛军打交道也很利索啊\N{\r英文}And you made quick work of those insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,不管是谁\N{\r英文}you're at the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.70,中文,,0,0,0,,推荐翻译专家，都会把你排在最前面\N{\r英文}of everyone's list when it comes to translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,而且你的单一范畴背景调查2年后才失效\N{\r英文}and you have another two years on your SSBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.38,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你仍有接触核心机密的许可\N{\r英文}so you still have top secret clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.26,中文,,0,0,0,,这也是我选择来你办公室，而不是伯克利的原因\N{\r英文}And that's why I'm in your office, and not at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.73,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我有东西想请你翻译\N{\r英文}I have something I need you to translate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.70,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你们为何而来？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Why are you here?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你们听得懂我们的话吗？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Can you understand us?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你们来自何方？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Where did you come from?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:24.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在听过了，有什么想法吗？\N{\r英文}Now you heard it, What do you make of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.58,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那就是...？  - 是的\N{\r英文}- Is that...?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 有几个？  - 什么几个？\N{\r英文}- How many?  - How many what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.31,中文,,0,0,0,,说话的有几个？\N{\r英文}How many speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.90,中文,,0,0,0,,2个\N{\r英文}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.98,中文,,0,0,0,,假设他们不是同时开口\N{\r英文}Assume they were not speaking at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你能肯定？他们有嘴吗？\N{\r英文}Are you sure? Do they have mouths?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你会如何来翻译这个？\N{\r英文}How would you approach translating this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你能分辨出词语，或者句子吗？\N{\r英文}You hear any words? Phrases?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我，我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.23,中文,,0,0,0,,那你能告诉我什么？\N{\r英文}So what can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的是，仅凭一个音频文件是做不出翻译的\N{\r英文}I can tell you that it's impossible to translate this from an audio file.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我得亲历现场与他们交谈\N{\r英文}I would need to be there to interact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你翻译波斯语时也没在现场啊\N{\r英文}You didn't need that for the Farsi translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,那是因为我已经掌握了波斯语，而这个...\N{\r英文}I didn't need it because I already knew the language. But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你打的什么主意\N{\r英文}I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.19,中文,,0,0,0,,- 揭穿我啊  - 我不会带你去蒙大拿\N{\r英文}- Tell me what I'm doing.  - I'm not taking you to Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,能接触核心机密就可以去参观，那不成了旅游景点了，我绝不会容许这发生\N{\r英文}It's all I can do to keep it from becoming a tourist site for anyone with TS clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是跟你讲明如何才能做好这份工作\N{\r英文}I'm just telling you what it would take to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是来跟你讨价还价的\N{\r英文}It is not a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:41.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我出了这个门，你的机会就没了\N{\r英文}If I leave here... your chance is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.83,中文,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\r英文}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.97,中文,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\r英文}Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚提到了伯克利，你接下来要找丹弗斯吧？\N{\r英文}You mentioned Berkeley. Are you going to ask Danvers next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\r英文}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.37,中文,,0,0,0,,在你邀请他前\N{\r英文}Before you commit to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:06.11,中文,,0,0,0,,问他梵文里的“战争”一词，以及翻译过来的意思\N{\r英文}ask him the Sanskrit word for "war" and its translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.74,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在中国和俄罗斯加入{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}An agreement on sharing scientific discoveries{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:21.30,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}联合国的磋商后，有望就共享科学发现达成协议{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}was closer tonight as Russia and China join talks at the United Nations.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:25.09,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}以此同时，全球金融市场陷入危机{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Meanwhile, financial markets across the world are in crisis{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:29.42,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}道琼斯工业指数狂泻2000点{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}with the Dow Jones industrial average fell 2,000 points...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.63,中文,,0,0,0,,- 早上好  - 上校？\N{\r英文}- Good Morning.  - Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.64,中文,,0,0,0,,“加维什提” 他说是争论的意思\N{\r英文}Gavisti. He said it means an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.15,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你的标准答案是？  - 寻找更多的牛\N{\r英文}- What do you say it means?  - A desire for more cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.65,中文,,0,0,0,,收拾好背包\N{\r英文}Pack your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.07,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好的，给我20分钟  - 我们10分钟后起飞\N{\r英文}- All right, give me twenty minutes.  - We take off in ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，请跟我来\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks! please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:36.15,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 没事\N{\r英文}- Are you all right?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.95,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.39,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，刚才听不清你说了什么\N{\r英文}Sorry. Couldn't hear what you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.87,中文,,0,0,0,,语言是文明的基石\N{\r英文}"Language is the foundation of civilization...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.63,中文,,0,0,0,,#是把人们聚到一起的粘合剂\N{\r英文}...It is the glue that holds the people together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.27,中文,,0,0,0,,也是冲突中最先使用的武器\N{\r英文}...It is the first weapon drawn in a conflict. "
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:32.85,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，这位是伊恩·唐纳利，路易丝·班克斯，伊恩·唐纳利\N{\r英文}Louise, this is Ian Donnelly. Louise Banks, Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.65,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这个见面礼不错嘛  - 是啊，你的大作\N{\r英文}- That's quite a greeting.  - Yeah...you wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.45,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.91,中文,,0,0,0,,序言都是这么写的\N{\r英文}It's the kind of thing you write as a preface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.06,中文,,0,0,0,,言简意赅，博取眼球\N{\r英文}Dazzle them with basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.36,中文,,0,0,0,,话是漂亮，可惜说错了\N{\r英文}It's great. Even if it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.78,中文,,0,0,0,,- 错了？  - 文明的基石并不是语言\N{\r英文}- It's wrong?  - The cornerstone of civilization isn't language,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.25,中文,,0,0,0,,而是科学\N{\r英文}it's science.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:55.47,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩是阿拉莫斯国家实验室的理论物理学家\N{\r英文}Ian is a theoretical physicist from Los Alamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你向我汇报工作，不过在“蛋壳”里时，你会和他搭配工作\N{\r英文}You will be reporting to me, but will be working with him when you are in the shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.02,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是这样叫不明飞行物的？\N{\r英文}Thats what they are calling the UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.60,中文,,0,0,0,,首要任务，搞清他们来自何方，来这里的目的\N{\r英文}Priority One. What do they want. Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:08.02,中文,,0,0,0,,除此之外，他们是如何过来的\N{\r英文}Beyond that, how did they get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他们掌握了超光速旅行吗？\N{\r英文}Are they capable of faster than light travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:14.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我专门列了个问题的单子\N{\r英文}I made a list of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.73,中文,,0,0,0,,从握手方式，到二进制序列\N{\r英文}you know, go over, start a series of handshakes to binary sequences...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,先别急着问他们各种问题\N{\r英文}How about we just talk to them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我们从简单交流开始，好吗？\N{\r英文}before we start throwing those problem at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.91,中文,,0,0,0,,这正是要你们两个的原因\N{\r英文}This is why you both are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我负责端咖啡\N{\r英文}I'll bring the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.78,中文,,0,0,0,,跟外星人一起喝咖啡\N{\r英文}Coffee with some aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.15,中文,,0,0,0,,- 带他们两个去凯特勒博士那  - 遵命，长官\N{\r英文}- I want you to take these two to Dr. Kettler.  - Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.85,中文,,0,0,0,,跟这位上尉去医务室\N{\r英文}Follow the Captain to the medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.62,中文,,0,0,0,,要花几分钟走下程序，之后我们就开工了\N{\r英文}The procedure should take just a few minutes, then we could start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.03,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r英文}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.80,中文,,0,0,0,,背包就交给他们保管吧，还有手机\N{\r英文}They will take care of your bags... and cell phones
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.84,中文,,0,0,0,,手机\N{\r英文}Cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.45,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\r英文}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.31,中文,,0,0,0,,带上这个，任何时候都别取\N{\r英文}Put this on and wear them all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.99,中文,,0,0,0,,长官，他们来了\N{\r英文}Sir, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.63,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝·班克斯，伊恩·唐纳利\N{\r英文}Louise Banks, Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你们上一次用餐是什么时候？\N{\r英文}When is the last time either of you have eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.49,中文,,0,0,0,,- 昨晚  - 我也一样\N{\r英文}- Last night.  - Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你们上一次做有精神压力的事，是什么时候？\N{\r英文}When was the last time you did something stressful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.91,中文,,0,0,0,,现在算吗？\N{\r英文}Does now count?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.64,中文,,0,0,0,,- 说说而已  - 刚刚...\N{\r英文}- Just saying.  - Who's being...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.22,中文,,0,0,0,,被抬出去的是谁？\N{\r英文}Carted off in a med-bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不是每个人都能承受这种经历\N{\r英文}Not everyone is able to process experiences like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要给你们抽点血\N{\r英文}I'm gonna get some blood from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.76,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再给你们打一针疫苗\N{\r英文}and give you an immunization dose to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:56.03,中文,,0,0,0,,来抵御各类细菌威胁，你们能签下这个吗？\N{\r英文}cover a battery of bacterial threats. Could you sign this please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.44,中文,,0,0,0,,请把袖子卷起来\N{\r英文}Roll up your sleeves, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你们都没有幽闭恐惧症吧？  - 没\N{\r英文}- Either of you claustrophobic?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.94,中文,,0,0,0,,有在服用什么药吗？对什么过敏吗？\N{\r英文}...taking any medication, allergies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,- 怀孕呢？  - 没有\N{\r英文}- Pregnant?  - NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.99,中文,,0,0,0,,加强剂的药效明显\N{\r英文}The booster is a kick to your system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.90,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你们可能会有不良反应\N{\r英文}so you may experience side effects:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.88,中文,,0,0,0,,诸如恶心，头晕，头疼\N{\r英文}like nausea, dizziness, headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.15,中文,,0,0,0,,或者耳鸣之类的\N{\r英文}A ringing in your ear like you have Tinnitus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.35,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在112分钟19秒后{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}In exactly 112 minutes and 19 seconds{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.66,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}重力会开始变化，直至从房间里消失{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}gravity starts to shift and slide out of the room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,对此你能做出科学上的解释吗？\N{\r英文}Have you found a scientific explanation for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:50.29,中文,,0,0,0,,- 比如这个变化是为了他们自己？  - 不，我觉得是照顾我们\N{\r英文}- Like is it for them?  - No, I think it is for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.21,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}似乎空气只在房间内流通，所以{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The air seems circulate inside the chamber, so...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.78,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}顶多两小时，氧气就耗尽了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}After about two hours, you run out of oxygen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:59.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那输送新鲜空气进房间，18个小时还不够吗？\N{\r英文}It doesn't take you eighteen hours to pump fresh air into a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,大气\N{\r英文}Atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:05.19,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么？  - 如果他们的大气\N{\r英文}- Excuse me?  - If their atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.59,中文,,0,0,0,,和地球上的不同\N{\r英文}is different from earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.52,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们每次打开大门前，就肯定需要数小时来平衡大气\N{\r英文}It would certainly take hours to be balanced two content...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:11.75,中文,,0,0,0,,制造适宜的压力来照顾我们\N{\r英文}pressure for us everytime they open their door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.11,中文,,0,0,0,,照你这么说，他们随时都可以闷死我们？\N{\r英文}So you're saying that they could suffocate us if they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.57,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是大卫·哈尔彭，中情局的特工\N{\r英文}This is Agent David Halpern, the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:20.55,中文,,0,0,0,,- 跟我去你们的工作地点吧  - 好的\N{\r英文}- Let me take you to your stations.  - Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.25,中文,,0,0,0,,记住，我们必须尽快搞清这些问题\N{\r英文}Remember, we need the answers as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.90,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来做什么，他们来自何方\N{\r英文}What they want, where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:27.89,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来这的目的，这是首先要解决的\N{\r英文}Why they are here, this is the priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.29,中文,,0,0,0,,大家听我说\N{\r英文}Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:31.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是伊恩·唐纳利博士，他负责带你们队\N{\r英文}This is Dr. Ian Donnelly, he will be runnig this team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.26,中文,,0,0,0,,他们有对什么做出回应吗，形状？模式？\N{\r英文}Have they responded to anything? Shapes, patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:36.75,中文,,0,0,0,,数字，斐波那契数列？\N{\r英文}numbers, Fibonacci?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们并不懂他们说的话，不过他们对“你好”有回应\N{\r英文}We can't tell what they were saying, but they responded to "hello", so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:42.26,中文,,0,0,0,,别急于求成就行\N{\r英文}Don't get ahead of youself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在有收获吗？\N{\r英文}What have you figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:48.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才刚开始而已    早上好各位\N{\r英文}We're just getting started. Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:51.54,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是路易丝·班克斯博士\N{\r英文}This is Dr. Louise Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.50,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她负责带你们队  - 班克斯博士，很荣幸\N{\r英文}- She will be heading your team. - Dr. Banks, its a pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.80,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士会接手沃勒博士的工作\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks is taking over the mission from Dr. Waller.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是15分钟警报\N{\r英文}That's 15 minute alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:02.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你该去穿衣做准备了\N{\r英文}You should have your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要进入何种辐射环境？\N{\r英文}What kind of radiation exposure are we walking into?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.02,中文,,0,0,0,,正常水平，这些只是以防万一\N{\r英文}Nominal. These are just for safety.
