Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,不过你们会适应的\N{\r英文}But you'll get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:53.19,中文,,0,0,0,,放到第二辆车上\N{\r英文}Load up in the second vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:02.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们几分钟后到\N{\r英文}We will be there in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.06,中文,,0,0,0,,都坐稳抓牢了\N{\r英文}Make sure you hold onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.51,0:25:16.58,中文,,0,0,0,,每隔18小时，飞船底部会打开扇门\N{\r英文}Every 18 hours... a door opens up at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.23,0:25:20.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就从那进去\N{\r英文}That's where we go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.24,0:27:54.92,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，这也行\N{\r英文}Yeah, that just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.63,0:28:18.29,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，出发吧，时间不等人\N{\r英文}Alright, lets move. Time is wasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.72,0:28:20.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？\N{\r英文}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:21.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\r英文}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:23.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我们上吧\N{\r英文}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.99,0:28:26.79,中文,,0,0,0,,秃鹫，我和马克上尉进去了，完毕\N{\r英文}Condor, I'm proceeding fast with Captain Marks, over
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.93,0:28:39.43,中文,,0,0,0,,一切正常，长官\N{\r英文}It's all good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.43,0:28:40.45,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你可以行动了  - 待命\N{\r英文}- You can proceed.  - Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.57,0:28:42.97,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，上来吧\N{\r英文}Okay, bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:28:56.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.22,0:29:01.62,中文,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.37,0:29:03.77,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.82,0:29:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你能行的，去吧\N{\r英文}You can do this. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.23,0:29:13.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我... 我觉得...\N{\r英文}I... I think...
