Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.82,0:29:41.06,中文,,0,0,0,,唐纳利博士，你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Dr. Donnelly, you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:48.30,中文,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\r英文}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.54,0:29:52.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\r英文}Holy fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.47,0:30:00.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我们去那里面\N{\r英文}We go down in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.64,0:30:02.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你们就可以开工了\N{\r英文}You can start your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.59,0:30:05.19,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 好的\N{\r英文}- OK.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.19,0:30:08.55,中文,,0,0,0,,- 全体前进  - 第一队已就位\N{\r英文}- Everybody, move up.  - Alpha Team in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:11.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们进去了\N{\r英文}We're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.89,0:31:02.57,中文,,0,0,0,,布置设备\N{\r英文}Setting up equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.38,0:31:38.21,中文,,0,0,0,,下面做什么？\N{\r英文}What happens now?
