Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.07,0:32:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.60,0:32:54.26,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.64,0:32:57.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以开始了\N{\r英文}You can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.64,0:33:17.74,中文,,0,0,0,,稍等一下\N{\r英文}Wait... Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.55,0:33:40.31,中文,,0,0,0,,要我走人吗？\N{\r英文}Am I fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.31,0:33:41.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你表现不错，比上一位强\N{\r英文}You were better than the last guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:45.34,中文,,0,0,0,,可我还是高兴不起来\N{\r英文}That doesn't make me feel any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.65,0:33:50.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你们在凌晨两点前要拿出方案来\N{\r英文}You both have till zero two hundred hours to figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.17,0:33:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好，那之后呢\N{\r英文}OK, what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.65,0:33:54.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你又回去\N{\r英文}You go back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:33.39,中文,,0,0,0,,UFO降临事件持续发酵，美国各地今日继续爆发各种骚乱\N{\r英文}Violence continues to spread across the US today in the wake of twelve landings.
