Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.63,0:34:38.48,中文,,0,0,0,,而国民警卫队未能遏止住\N{\r英文}and the crack down by the National Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.48,0:34:41.66,中文,,0,0,0,,全国各地连续三晚的抢掠行为\N{\r英文}Failed to prevent a third night of looting across the country.
