Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.86,0:34:49.45,中文,,0,0,0,,里面的144名成员恐生还无望\N{\r英文}are feared dead after they set their compound ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.45,0:34:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的网站上宣称，外星人的降临\N{\r英文}Their website claims, the arrival of aliens
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:54.60,中文,,0,0,0,,是预言里12...\N{\r英文}Set in motion a prophecy that twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:17.13,中文,,0,0,0,,15分钟后我们又要进去了，你有什么新情报吗？\N{\r英文}Uh.. we're up in fifteen... You got any new intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.14,0:35:19.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我们在回放一些他们的声音\N{\r英文}Yeah. We've been playing back some of their sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.55,0:35:21.99,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么进展吗？\N{\r英文}And where has that got you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.42,0:35:25.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他们播放音频回应我们时，声源不明\N{\r英文}When they play audio back at us. It's from an unseen source
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.27,0:35:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你在研究些什么？\N{\r英文}What are you up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.91,0:35:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,就房间里的谈话，还有从对话里随意挑选的片段\N{\r英文}Huh, just conversations from the room, and random branches of dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.68,0:35:35.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一无所获\N{\r英文}We have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:02.60,中文,,0,0,0,,氧气瓶状态：1到6皆满
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.10,0:36:07.40,中文,,0,0,0,,距“蛋壳”开启还有9分钟\N{\r英文}T-minus nine minutes till shell activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.80,0:36:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,距“蛋壳”开启还有9分钟\N{\r英文}T-minus nine minutes till shell activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.42,0:36:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那个做什么用的？  - 涂写用的\N{\r英文}- What's that for?  - A visual aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.44,0:36:16.69,中文,,0,0,0,,听着，他们不开口的话，我一辈子都甭想学会\N{\r英文}Look, I'm never gonna be able to speak their words,
