Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.35,0:36:20.29,中文,,0,0,0,,可要是他们有文字之类的\N{\r英文}But they might have some sort of written language
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:23.71,中文,,0,0,0,,或简单的涂写交流方式\N{\r英文}or basis for visual communication.
