Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.84,0:37:11.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我是人类\N{\r英文}I'm human.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.62,0:37:14.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你是什么？\N{\r英文}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.30,0:37:27.38,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.17,0:38:19.69,中文,,0,0,0,,- 天啊  - 你录下来了吗？\N{\r英文}- Oh my God.  - Are you recording this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.69,0:38:21.85,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，长官，我已经发回大本营了\N{\r英文}Yes sir. I tape this back to base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.07,0:38:26.90,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，真难以置信啊\N{\r英文}Louise, it's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.66,0:38:43.33,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.87,0:38:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.37,0:38:49.10,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.16,0:39:03.13,中文,,0,0,0,,很好... 慢点啊\N{\r英文}OK, slow down please...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.27,0:39:24.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是想否认你取得的成果\N{\r英文}I don't want to take away from your success yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.70,0:39:27.80,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，就只有这一招了吗？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks, is it really the right approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.80,0:39:30.83,中文,,0,0,0,,交他们读书认字？\N{\r英文}Try to teach them how to speak and read?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.50,0:39:33.81,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这得花多久啊  - 你不懂\N{\r英文}- That's gonna take longer.  - You're wrong.
