Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.13,0:39:39.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你在这里做的每件事\N{\r英文}Everything you're doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.64,0:39:42.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我都要给一屋子的人解释\N{\r英文}I have to explain to a room full of men,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.01,0:39:43.89,中文,,0,0,0,,而他们只关心一个问题\N{\r英文}whose first and last question...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.89,0:39:45.86,中文,,0,0,0,,这会给我们带来怎样的麻烦\N{\r英文}is how can this be used against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.13,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你得给我令人信服的理由\N{\r英文}So you'll have to give me more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.12,0:39:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,袋鼠\N{\r英文}Kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.38,0:39:53.78,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.29,0:39:55.87,中文,,0,0,0,,1770年\N{\r英文}In 1770,
