Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.06,0:40:07.75,中文,,0,0,0,,在地上蹦来蹦去的动物\N{\r英文}that hop around with their babies in their pouches,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.75,0:40:11.31,中文,,0,0,0,,问它们叫什么，土著回答“Kanguru”\N{\r英文}And he asked what they were. And the Aborigines said "Kanguru".
