Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.61,0:40:20.00,中文,,0,0,0,,“我听不懂”，所以...\N{\r英文}"I don't understand". So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.01,0:40:22.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我在房间里用这个是为了化解误会\N{\r英文}I need this so that we don't misinterpret things in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,不然得耗费10倍的时间\N{\r英文}otherwise this is ganna take 10 times as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:29.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这理由勉强能交差\N{\r英文}I can sell that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.13,0:40:32.26,中文,,0,0,0,,下次对话前，你必须把要用的词\N{\r英文}I need you to submit your vocabulary of words...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.26,0:40:33.78,中文,,0,0,0,,拟个单子给我\N{\r英文}before the next session.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.05,0:40:37.25,中文,,0,0,0,,请别忘了土著人的遭遇\N{\r英文}And remember what happened to the Aborigines.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.84,0:40:41.03,中文,,0,0,0,,一个更先进的种族差点令他们灭亡\N{\r英文}A more advanced race nearly wiped them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:51.91,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你讲的故事不错  - 谢谢\N{\r英文}- Its a good story.  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.71,0:40:56.17,中文,,0,0,0,,是杜撰的，但管用就行\N{\r英文}It's not true, but it proves my point.
