Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.08,0:41:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,...我们设法还原出一些素数序列\N{\r英文}...we being able to produce some prime number sequences back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.54,0:41:22.01,中文,,0,0,0,,- 也算是有收获  - 祝贺你，学到鹦鹉的本事了\N{\r英文}- So that's something.  - Congratulations, you're a parrot.
