Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.07,0:41:51.26,中文,,0,0,0,,他主宰着局势走向，不管尚做什么\N{\r英文}...for him is a big domino, whatever Shang does
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.26,0:41:53.89,中文,,0,0,0,,最少也会有4个国家效仿\N{\r英文}at least four other nations would follow.
