Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.32,0:42:08.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你要教他们认识你和伊恩的名字？\N{\r英文}You're going to teach them your name? And Ian's?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.72,0:42:11.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，他们有名字的话，也会教给我们\N{\r英文}Yes, so we can learn their names. If they have names,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.64,0:42:13.66,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再介绍代词\N{\r英文}and then introduce pronouns later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.15,0:42:16.42,中文,,0,0,0,,这些都是小学教的\N{\r英文}These are all grade-school words.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.42,0:42:18.82,中文,,0,0,0,,吃，走\N{\r英文}Eat, walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.39,0:42:22.09,中文,,0,0,0,,给我解释下\N{\r英文}Help me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.86,0:42:29.72,中文,,0,0,0,,别，别擦，别擦上面的\N{\r英文}No no no! Not the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.62,0:42:34.22,中文,,0,0,0,,“你们到访地球的目的？”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.26,0:42:37.51,中文,,0,0,0,,好，这就是你想问的，对吧？\N{\r英文}OK, this is where you want to get to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.51,0:42:38.91,中文,,0,0,0,,- 就是这个  - 好\N{\r英文}- That is the question.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.91,0:42:43.51,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们首先要确定，他们懂得什么是“问题”\N{\r英文}So, first we need to make sure that they understand what a question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.90,0:42:47.75,中文,,0,0,0,,本质是我们发起请求\N{\r英文}The nature of our request for information...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.75,0:42:49.27,中文,,0,0,0,,来获取信息\N{\r英文}along with response.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:52.25,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我们还得解释清楚\N{\r英文}Then we need to clarify
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.25,0:42:54.96,中文,,0,0,0,,“你”跟“你们”有什么\N{\r英文}the difference between a specific "you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.97,0:42:56.73,中文,,0,0,0,,区别\N{\r英文}and a collective "you".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.73,0:43:01.23,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们并不关心某个外星人被派来做什么\N{\r英文}Because we don't want to know why a 'Joe' alien is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.23,0:43:04.05,中文,,0,0,0,,而是想搞清他们共同到访的目的\N{\r英文}we want to know why they all landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.05,0:43:07.56,中文,,0,0,0,,而目的又需要懂得意图\N{\r英文}And purpose requires an understanding of intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.56,0:43:10.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得搞清这是他们自觉的选择\N{\r英文}We need to find out do they make conscious choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.31,0:43:12.74,中文,,0,0,0,,亦或是受本能驱使\N{\r英文}or is the motivation so instinctive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.74,0:43:15.54,中文,,0,0,0,,以至于对提问根本不会有反应\N{\r英文}that they don't understand any why question at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.54,0:43:19.75,中文,,0,0,0,,而重中之重，我们得跟他们建立起足够的词汇量\N{\r英文}And biggest of all we need to have enough vocabulary with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.75,0:43:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,能让我们明白他们的回答\N{\r英文}that we understand their answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.90,0:43:25.40,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.84,0:43:27.74,中文,,0,0,0,,遵照你的单子\N{\r英文}Stick to your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.21,0:43:29.98,中文,,0,0,0,,千万...\N{\r英文}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.44,0:43:33.17,中文,,0,0,0,,别乱加词进去\N{\r英文}Don't add anything to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.24,0:43:58.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我们出发吧\N{\r英文}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.10,0:44:09.79,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.20,0:44:12.28,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，我叫路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise, I'm Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.21,0:44:20.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.66,0:44:24.97,中文,,0,0,0,,那是新符号吗？我分不清\N{\r英文}Is that a new symbol? I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.97,0:44:27.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧，我觉得还是表示“人类”的符号\N{\r英文}I don't know, I think its the symbol for "human" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.62,0:44:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,只是收尾处略弯了点\N{\r英文}Just a little curl at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.04,0:44:33.21,中文,,0,0,0,,或许这表示提问，我也不敢肯定\N{\r英文}Maybe they indicate a question. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.81,0:44:37.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我也一样，路易丝，我觉得他们没明白\N{\r英文}I don't know, Louise, I think they got confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.42,0:44:40.61,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，我们继续下一个词吧\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks, now we should move to the next word.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.91,0:45:01.41,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.06,0:45:04.71,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没事的  - 什么情况？\N{\r英文}- It's okay.  - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.71,0:45:06.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\r英文}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.71,0:45:08.61,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我没事  - 你疯了吗？\N{\r英文}- Yeah, I'm fine.  - Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.95,0:45:10.67,中文,,0,0,0,,得让他们见到我的真面目\N{\r英文}They need to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.68,0:45:12.69,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她要脱掉核生化防护服  - 班克斯博士！\N{\r英文}- She's taking off the HAZMAT suit.  - Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.04,0:45:18.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？你有感染的危险\N{\r英文}Are you OK? You're risking contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.32,0:45:20.93,中文,,0,0,0,,- 得让他们见到我的真面目  - 班克斯博士\N{\r英文}- They need to see me.  - Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.36,0:45:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,- 班克斯博士  - 她朝玻璃墙走去了\N{\r英文}- Dr. Banks.  - She's walking toward the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.26,0:45:28.94,中文,,0,0,0,,要终止任务吗？\N{\r英文}Should we abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.58,0:45:33.68,中文,,0,0,0,,回到你们的位置\N{\r英文}Go back to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.28,0:46:50.74,中文,,0,0,0,,这才算是正式见面\N{\r英文}Now that's a proper introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.16,0:47:04.89,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.42,0:47:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我叫路易丝\N{\r英文}I'm Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.54,0:47:12.38,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，你不介绍自己吗？\N{\r英文}Ian, you want to introduce yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.11,0:47:17.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我... 好吧\N{\r英文}I... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.19,0:47:21.79,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.39,0:47:27.29,中文,,0,0,0,,豁出去了\N{\r英文}Screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.30,0:47:34.11,中文,,0,0,0,,人都有一死，对吧？\N{\r英文}Everybody dies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.04,0:47:38.86,中文,,0,0,0,,长官，唐纳利也脱掉了防护服\N{\r英文}Sir, Donnelly is taking off his HAZMAT suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.86,0:47:40.38,中文,,0,0,0,,准许终止任务？\N{\r英文}Permission to abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.09,0:47:42.97,中文,,0,0,0,,继续对话进程\N{\r英文}Continue the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.85,0:48:00.68,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩\N{\r英文}Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.68,0:48:02.59,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.49,0:48:05.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\r英文}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.41,0:48:08.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你们叫什么？\N{\r英文}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.38,0:48:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,这应该是他们的名字\N{\r英文}I think those are their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.70,0:48:42.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他们也有名字\N{\r英文}They have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.70,0:48:44.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们该如何称呼他们呢？\N{\r英文}So what are we gonna call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.51,0:48:47.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.89,0:48:50.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我推荐阿波特和科斯特洛\N{\r英文}I was thinking of Abbott and Costello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.49,0:48:51.69,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿波特和科斯特洛是1940到1950年间好莱坞著名的喜剧搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.93,0:48:54.69,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.25,0:48:56.78,中文,,0,0,0,,好，很好\N{\r英文}Yeah. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.88,0:49:00.32,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\r英文}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.15,0:49:19.92,中文,,0,0,0,,一队人员，下车后直接前往污染物净化室\N{\r英文}Team one, exit your vehicle and proceed directly into the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.97,0:49:30.33,中文,,0,0,0,,在进入设备间前，请别取下你们的面罩\N{\r英文}Leave your respirators on until you reach equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.38,0:50:12.23,中文,,0,0,0,,二队人员，下车后直接前往污染物净化室\N{\r英文}Team two, exit your vehicles, continue to the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.65,0:50:15.27,中文,,0,0,0,,在进入设备间前\N{\r英文}Leave your respirators on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.28,0:50:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,千万别取下你们的面罩\N{\r英文}and do not ... until you reach the equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.53,0:50:25.67,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你感觉如何？  - 疲劳过度\N{\r英文}- How do you feel?  - Overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.47,0:50:29.93,中文,,0,0,0,,不用我说你也明白，这样做有多危险\N{\r英文}Like I said, I don't need to tell you, you put yourself at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.37,0:50:34.23,中文,,0,0,0,,并没有辐射中毒的迹象\N{\r英文}There is no signs of radiation poisoning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.23,0:50:36.39,中文,,0,0,0,,等你的血检出来后，我们再确认\N{\r英文}We'll see how your blood tests look.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.75,0:50:39.11,中文,,0,0,0,,- 目前嘛，我再给你打一针加强剂  - 好\N{\r英文}- For now, Im gonna give you another boost.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.85,0:50:44.37,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没有辐射中毒？  - 我们没查出任何异样\N{\r英文}- No radiation?  - Nothing else we can detect either.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.37,0:50:46.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不过为了以防外一，我还是给她打了加强剂\N{\r英文}But I give her a strong cocktail regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.37,0:50:49.05,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们头一回取得实质进展\N{\r英文}It's the first time we made significant progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.31,0:50:54.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们就冒这一回险\N{\r英文}All right. We'll take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.27,0:50:58.17,中文,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝...宝贝  - 那边到底什么情况？\N{\r英文}- Honey...honey.  - What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.17,0:51:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你一个字都不能透露？  - 我没事\N{\r英文}- Is there anything you can tell me?  - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.29,0:51:04.35,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你不用担心，好吗？  - 我怎么能不担心？\N{\r英文}- You don't need to worry. OK?  - How can I not worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.35,0:51:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,冷静点，好吗\N{\r英文}Just calm down. Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.31,0:51:10.72,中文,,0,0,0,,贝基吵着问我，那些怪物会不会把爹地杀了\N{\r英文}Becky asked me if the monsters are going to kill Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.73,0:51:13.23,中文,,0,0,0,,宝贝，那是不可能的\N{\r英文}Honey, it's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.87,0:51:18.73,中文,,0,0,0,,- 一定要注意安全  - 不用担心\N{\r英文}- Just stay safe.  - No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.73,0:51:21.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我好害怕\N{\r英文}I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.29,0:52:37.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我们仍然对七肢桶\N{\r英文}Here are some of the many things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.19,0:52:39.23,中文,,0,0,0,,的许多方面一无所知\N{\r英文}we don't know about the heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.23,0:52:42.45,中文,,0,0,0,,hepta源自古希腊语，表示七，pod，表示脚\N{\r英文}Greek hepta, "seven", pod, "foot".
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.45,0:52:45.19,中文,,0,0,0,,七只脚，故称七肢桶\N{\r英文}Seven feet. heptapod.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.89,0:52:48.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是何方神圣？\N{\r英文}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.47,0:52:53.70,中文,,0,0,0,,试图从任何有意义的角度来回答，都困难重重\N{\r英文}Trying to answer this in any meaningful way is hampered by the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.71,0:52:56.43,中文,,0,0,0,,因为外界既看不到、也听不到他们\N{\r英文}outside being able to see them and hear them,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.43,0:52:59.35,中文,,0,0,0,,七肢桶不留下任何蛛丝马迹\N{\r英文}The heptapod leave absolutely no footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.07,0:53:04.09,中文,,0,0,0,,他们宇宙飞船的化学组成仍未可知\N{\r英文}The chemical composition of their spaceship is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.41,0:53:08.03,中文,,0,0,0,,“蛋壳”不产生废物，不排出气体，也没有辐射\N{\r英文}The Shell makes no waste, no gas, no radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.61,0:53:11.25,中文,,0,0,0,,假设“蛋壳”之间有互有通讯\N{\r英文}Assuming that the shell is communicating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:13.51,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们手段高明，悄无声息\N{\r英文}They do so without detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.51,0:53:15.93,中文,,0,0,0,,“蛋壳”内的空气不会被\N{\r英文}The air between the shells is untroubled...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.94,0:53:18.27,中文,,0,0,0,,超声波或光波干扰\N{\r英文}by sonic emissions or light waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.05,0:53:23.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是科学家，还是观光客？\N{\r英文}Are they scientists... or tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.01,0:53:26.57,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是科学家的话，为什么提问并不积极\N{\r英文}If they're scientists, they don't seem to ask a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.39,0:53:31.35,中文,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要停在现在的地方？\N{\r英文}Why they park where they did?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.05,0:53:34.79,中文,,0,0,0,,#世界上最富盛名的专家也是一头雾水\N{\r英文}The world's most decorated experts can't figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.67,0:53:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,最受推崇的理论是，他们选择的地点都是\N{\r英文}The most plausible theory is that they chose places on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.57,0:53:40.97,中文,,0,0,0,,地球上闪电出现机率最低的\N{\r英文}with the lowest incidences of lightning strikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.47,0:53:43.40,中文,,0,0,0,,可也有个别例外\N{\r英文}But there are exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.41,0:53:46.15,中文,,0,0,0,,另一种候选理论是，这些地点都跟上世纪80年代\N{\r英文}The second most plausible theory is that Sheena Easton...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.15,0:53:48.62,中文,,0,0,0,,席娜·伊斯顿的流行歌曲有关\N{\r英文}had a hit song in each of these sites in 1980.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.82,0:53:48.62,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}席娜·伊斯顿：苏格兰著名歌星
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.62,0:53:50.61,中文,,0,0,0,,所以... 我们只是瞎猜\N{\r英文}So... we just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.05,0:53:54.59,中文,,0,0,0,,他们之间如何交流？\N{\r英文}How do they communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.53,0:53:57.97,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝在这的工作，令我们自惭形秽\N{\r英文}Here, Louise just put us all to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.67,0:54:02.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我们取得的首个突破是发现七肢桶\N{\r英文}The first breakthrough was discovered that there is no correlation...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.33,0:54:06.25,中文,,0,0,0,,的书写和口语之间并无关联\N{\r英文}between what a heptapod says and what a heptapod writes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.61,0:54:24.31,中文,,0,0,0,,不像任何人类文字\N{\r英文}Unlike all written human language.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.31,0:54:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的书写是会意象形语标文字\N{\r英文}Their writing is semasiographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.57,0:54:29.85,中文,,0,0,0,,只传达意思，并无对应的发音\N{\r英文}It conveyes meaning, it doesn't represent sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.89,0:54:38.77,中文,,0,0,0,,或许我们的书写，在他们看来是多余的\N{\r英文}Perhaps they view our form of writing as a wasted oppurtunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.39,0:54:41.89,中文,,0,0,0,,浪费了第二个交流渠道\N{\r英文}Passing at a second communications channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:49.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要感谢巴基斯坦的朋友\N{\r英文}We have our friends in Pakistan to thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.35,0:54:51.87,中文,,0,0,0,,他们贡献了对七肢桶书写的研究\N{\r英文}For their study on how the heptapods write.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.09,0:54:54.76,中文,,0,0,0,,因为和说话不同\N{\r英文}Because unlike speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.77,0:54:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,语标不受时间限制\N{\r英文}a logogram is free of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.77,0:55:02.59,中文,,0,0,0,,与他们的飞船、身体相似\N{\r英文}Like their ship or their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:05.87,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的书写文字不存在前后顺序\N{\r英文}their written language has no forward or backward direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.33,0:55:09.67,中文,,0,0,0,,语言学家称之为非线性拼写\N{\r英文}Linguists call this nonlinear orthography.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.67,0:55:13.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这不禁让人疑问：“他们也是这样思考的吗？”\N{\r英文}Which raises the question: "Is this how they think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.09,0:55:17.07,中文,,0,0,0,,想象你要用双手写一个句子\N{\r英文}Imagine you wanted to write a sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.07,0:55:19.41,中文,,0,0,0,,同时从2头开始\N{\r英文}using 2 hands, starting from either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.55,0:55:23.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你得想好要写的每一个字\N{\r英文}You have to know each word you want to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.25,0:55:25.93,中文,,0,0,0,,以及它们占用的空间\N{\r英文}as well as how much space they will occupy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.19,0:55:30.47,中文,,0,0,0,,而七肢桶在2秒内就能轻松写出\N{\r英文}A heptapod can write a complex sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.47,0:55:32.46,中文,,0,0,0,,一个复杂的句子\N{\r英文}in two seconds effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.47,0:55:35.43,中文,,0,0,0,,而我们做个最简单的回复，都要花上一个月\N{\r英文}It's taking us a month to make a simplest reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.83,0:55:38.86,中文,,0,0,0,,下一步，扩充词汇量\N{\r英文}Next, expand the vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.87,0:55:42.47,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝认为怎么都要花上一个月\N{\r英文}Louse thinks it could easily take another month to be ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.59,0:56:00.99,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r英文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.21,0:56:05.15,中文,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 韦伯正找你呢\N{\r英文}- Hey. - Weber's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.17,0:56:08.61,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，你以为我躲在这干嘛？\N{\r英文}Yeah, why do you think I'm hiding out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.89,0:56:11.51,中文,,0,0,0,,上来啊\N{\r英文}Come on, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.25,0:56:22.09,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这地方不错吧？  - 嗯，风景不错\N{\r英文}- Nice out here, huh?  - Yeah, it's a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.03,0:56:24.79,中文,,0,0,0,,远离喧嚣\N{\r英文}Away from the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.73,0:56:30.31,中文,,0,0,0,,其实，我刚好想到你\N{\r英文}You know, I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.83,0:56:36.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你处理语言的方式挺像数学家，你自己也知道吧？\N{\r英文}You approach language like a mathematician. You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.69,0:56:41.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我就当你是恭维我啊\N{\r英文}I will take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.25,0:56:42.99,中文,,0,0,0,,就是恭维\N{\r英文}Well, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.65,0:56:46.23,中文,,0,0,0,,多亏了你\N{\r英文}And... I watch you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.23,0:56:48.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才能避开那些沟通陷阱\N{\r英文}steer us around these communication traps
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.77,0:56:50.78,中文,,0,0,0,,不然我还蒙在鼓里\N{\r英文}that I didn't even know existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.79,0:56:52.33,中文,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\r英文}What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.67,0:56:56.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我单身就是这个原因吧\N{\r英文}I guess that's why I'm single.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.47,0:56:59.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不是打击你，懂得去沟通还不足以\N{\r英文}Trust me, you can understand communication
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.81,0:57:01.49,中文,,0,0,0,,让你脱单啊\N{\r英文}and still end up single.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.67,0:57:13.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我总觉得那里面发生的一切\N{\r英文}I feel like everything that happens in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.29,0:57:16.27,中文,,0,0,0,,都和我们俩有关\N{\r英文}comes down to the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.99,0:57:22.13,中文,,0,0,0,,这是好事，对吧？你和我？\N{\r英文}It's a good thing, right? You and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.19,0:57:28.49,中文,,0,0,0,,整天和些废物一起工作，你也受不了吧？\N{\r英文}You see those jokers that we are working with?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.97,0:57:30.89,中文,,0,0,0,,能遇到你，真是老天有眼\N{\r英文}Thank God, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.93,0:57:36.73,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}外星人危机 第25天 委内瑞拉{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.68,0:57:39.65,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}外星人危机 第25天 塞拉利昂{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.75,0:57:41.49,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}伦敦  拯救我们的种族！{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.49,0:57:45.07,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚，第一张外星人的照片开始疯传\N{\r英文}Tonight, the first photograph of the aliens goes viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.89,0:57:48.57,中文,,0,0,0,,环保组织警告，蒙大拿存在的\N{\r英文}Biological contamination is a major risk factor
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.57,0:57:52.23,中文,,0,0,0,,主要风险因子就是生化污染\N{\r英文}At the Montana site. So say environmental pressure groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.23,0:57:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,在华盛顿，80万市民走上街头\N{\r英文}800,000 march on Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.45,0:57:57.21,中文,,0,0,0,,抗议政府的危机应对\N{\r英文}to protest the government's handling on the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.21,0:57:59.91,中文,,0,0,0,,别走开，还有更多的特别报道\N{\r英文}All this and more special coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.23,0:58:04.21,中文,,0,0,0,,...有人在那东西里和外星人接触\N{\r英文}...first contact was whoever is inside that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.21,0:58:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,猜猜是谁在导演？当然是政府啊\N{\r英文}and who do we have running the show? The government, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.79,0:58:10.77,中文,,0,0,0,,就是这个政府搞砸了我们的医疗保险，搞垮了我们的军队\N{\r英文}The same government who ruined our health care and bankrupted our military.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.77,0:58:14.06,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这些人，他们大多数人连枪都没有\N{\r英文}Look at these people! Most of them don't even have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.07,0:58:16.25,中文,,0,0,0,,面对着可能的全面入侵\N{\r英文}We could be facing a full-scale invasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.25,0:58:19.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的总统却一味忍让和绥靖\N{\r英文}and our president is just willing to sit back and let them take our country
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.99,0:58:22.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就要完蛋了，醒醒吧大家！\N{\r英文}We are falling asleep at the wheel, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.71,0:58:24.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你们知道我说的是事实，肯定知道\N{\r英文}You know what I'm talking about. I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.71,0:58:29.09,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该展现武力，威慑对方，这才是上上策\N{\r英文}The smartest thing we could do right now would be to give them a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.09,0:58:31.09,中文,,0,0,0,,最好是向他们发出警告\N{\r英文}I'm talking about a shot across the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.09,0:58:34.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我想了解听众朋友的观点，请拨打热线电话，发表下你对目前局势的看法\N{\r英文}I wonder what would you think, call the number you already know, what do you think all about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.29,0:59:02.97,中文,,0,0,0,,这个词怎么念？\N{\r英文}What's this word?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.79,0:59:21.79,中文,,0,0,0,,行星\N{\r英文}Planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.67,0:59:29.43,中文,,0,0,0,,比方说，地球是颗行星\N{\r英文}That's like... the Earth is a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.09,0:59:32.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我在加略特老师课上做的东西，你要看吗？\N{\r英文}Want to see my project from Mrs. Garriott class?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.11,0:59:34.69,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊，小肉鼻\N{\r英文}Yes, little-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.99,0:59:40.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要做自己的电视节目\N{\r英文}We had to make up our own TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.81,0:59:42.67,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们有的话\N{\r英文}If we had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.37,0:59:46.21,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这两个人是谁？  - 你和爸爸\N{\r英文}- Who are those two people?  - That's you and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.61,0:59:49.71,中文,,0,0,0,,节目叫“爸爸妈妈与动物交谈”\N{\r英文}The show is called: "Mommy and Daddy talk to animals."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.73,0:59:53.17,中文,,0,0,0,,真有爱\N{\r英文}It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.57,0:59:58.99,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.93,1:00:06.67,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你有权不开心，因为你爸爸和我...  - 我懂，我没事\N{\r英文}- You know, it's okay to be sad that your dad and I...  - I know. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.93,1:00:10.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我们俩都很爱你\N{\r英文}We both love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.93,1:00:13.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我懂，这只是幅卡通，不代表什么\N{\r英文}I know. It's just a cartoon, not real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.62,1:00:15.10,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝？\N{\r英文}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.47,1:00:21.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\r英文}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.62,1:00:25.20,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，没什么\N{\r英文}Yeah... yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.52,1:00:29.30,中文,,0,0,0,,就是我想给你解释，也可能会\N{\r英文}I'm not sure it's something I can...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.76,1:00:31.21,中文,,0,0,0,,力不从心\N{\r英文}I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.22,1:00:32.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你没去凯文医生那检查下吗？\N{\r英文}When was your last check with Dr. Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.97,1:00:35.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\r英文}I'm ok.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.30,1:00:39.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我出去透透气，不用担心\N{\r英文}I'll get some air, I'm ok.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.29,1:01:42.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉好些了吗？\N{\r英文}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.14,1:01:49.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要补充睡眠，不过...\N{\r英文}I need some sleep, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.72,1:01:51.15,中文,,0,0,0,,还挺得住\N{\r英文}I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.76,1:01:53.56,中文,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\r英文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.24,1:01:58.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我最近在研读一种理论，里面讲到\N{\r英文}I've been doing a bit of reading about this idea that...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.90,1:02:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你全身心的钻研一门外语\N{\r英文}if you immerse yourself into a foreign language...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.48,1:02:06.51,中文,,0,0,0,,- 整个人都会骤然改变  - 嗯，是萨丕尔-沃夫假说\N{\r英文}- You can actually rewire your brain.  - It's the the Sapir-Whorf, a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.59,1:02:09.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这种理论\N{\r英文}It is a theory that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.56,1:02:11.73,中文,,0,0,0,,这种理论认为\N{\r英文}It is the theory that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.73,1:02:15.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你所讲的语言能决定你的思维模式\N{\r英文}The language you speak determines how you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.26,1:02:18.66,中文,,0,0,0,,对，这能影响到你的世界观\N{\r英文}Yes, it affects how you see everything... it was...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.47,1:02:23.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我想问下，你做梦都在说他们的语言吗？\N{\r英文}I'm curious. Are you dreaming in their language?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.20,1:02:35.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我是做过这样的梦，可我觉得...\N{\r英文}I've had a few dreams, but I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.74,1:02:41.19,中文,,0,0,0,,并不会因此而误了工作\N{\r英文}I don't think that makes me unfit to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.78,1:03:03.61,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你有睡觉吗？  - 睡了会儿\N{\r英文}- Did you sleep?  - A little.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.34,1:03:06.31,中文,,0,0,0,,你懂中文吗?\N{\r英文}You know Mandarin?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.25,1:03:22.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你马上要听的声音是来自中国军队的最高统帅\N{\r英文}The voice you're about to hear belongs to the Chinese military chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.25,1:03:26.06,中文,,0,0,0,,尚将军\N{\r英文}General Shang.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.61,1:03:28.23,中文,,0,0,0,,戴上耳机\N{\r英文}Put it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.88,1:03:34.17,中文,,0,0,0,,这有卫星信号，你边看边听，确定他在跟谁说话\N{\r英文}We got satellite feed, hear who he's talking to, if you would look.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.54,1:03:37.05,中文,,0,0,0,,往回倒\N{\r英文}Please go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.50,1:03:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,停\N{\r英文}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.03,1:03:45.65,中文,,0,0,0,,他说这12艘船都会给我们先进技术\N{\r英文}He's saying that each of the twelve is offering advanced technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.43,1:03:50.60,中文,,0,0,0,,再回倒，播放\N{\r英文}Go back again and play.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.04,1:03:57.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他手下的科学家团队正尝试破译\N{\r英文}His science team is attempting to decode the...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.28,1:04:00.76,中文,,0,0,0,,“感觉”，“感觉”？我不明白是什么意思\N{\r英文}"sense", "sense"? I dont know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.43,1:04:03.18,中文,,0,0,0,,能获取优势之类的\N{\r英文}Something that advantage...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.19,1:04:07.28,中文,,0,0,0,,西服，荣誉，花朵，我不...\N{\r英文}Suits, honor and flowers. I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.55,1:04:12.27,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我不明白，抱歉了  - 我也搞不明白\N{\r英文}- I don't know, that's all. - I don't know what it means either.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.63,1:04:15.22,中文,,0,0,0,,一小时前，中国的军队开始集结\N{\r英文}An hour ago, China mobilized forces...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.56,1:04:17.89,中文,,0,0,0,,现在俄罗斯也响应了\N{\r英文}and now Russia is following suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.89,1:04:19.91,中文,,0,0,0,,尚打定主意要行动了\N{\r英文}Shang is about to start something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.47,1:04:22.74,中文,,0,0,0,,都是一样的西装... 西装...\N{\r英文}All same suits... Suits...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.98,1:04:27.17,中文,,0,0,0,,是序数牌，字牌，花牌\N{\r英文}suits, honor, flowers...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.17,1:04:29.84,中文,,0,0,0,,上校，这些都是麻将里的牌\N{\r英文}Colonel, those are all tile sets in Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.63,1:04:33.14,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊，难道他们\N{\r英文}God... are they...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.64,1:04:36.81,中文,,0,0,0,,他们在用游戏和七肢桶沟通吗？\N{\r英文}Are they are using a game to converse with the Heptapods?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.66,1:04:40.25,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能...这又如何？\N{\r英文}Maybe... why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.41,1:04:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,假如我不教英语，而是教七肢桶国际象棋\N{\r英文}Let's say I taught them chess instead of English.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.11,1:04:48.42,中文,,0,0,0,,通过游戏来进行每句对话，在对弈的过程中传递每个想法\N{\r英文}Every conversation would be a game, every idea expressed through opposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.43,1:04:50.85,中文,,0,0,0,,只有胜负之分，你还不明白？\N{\r英文}Victory... defeat. You see the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.83,1:04:54.54,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我只给你把锤子\N{\r英文}If all I ever gave you was a hammer...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.92,1:04:56.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你看什么都像钉子\N{\r英文}Everything is a nail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.28,1:05:00.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须问关键问题\N{\r英文}We need to ask the big question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.80,1:05:03.38,中文,,0,0,0,,等不了了\N{\r英文}Ready or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.53,1:05:52.25,中文,,0,0,0,,“七肢桶 目的”\N{\r英文}“heptapods purpose”
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.16,1:06:05.99,中文,,0,0,0,,“七肢桶 目的 地球” 你们来地球的目的？\N{\r英文}“heptapods purpose Earth” What is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.94,1:06:14.69,中文,,0,0,0,,只有科斯特洛一人？\N{\r英文}Do we only have Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.59,1:06:21.33,中文,,0,0,0,,很好，你出现了\N{\r英文}OK. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.84,1:06:45.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他说了什么？\N{\r英文}What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.68,1:06:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,给武器\N{\r英文}Offer weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.16,1:07:01.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你可是亲眼看到他们写的\N{\r英文}But you saw what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.72,1:07:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,用的那个词他们还没完全搞明白\N{\r英文}Using a word that they don't fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.62,1:07:05.87,中文,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\r英文}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.87,1:07:07.57,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.57,1:07:09.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们并不知道他们\N{\r英文}We don't know if they understand
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.96,1:07:12.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是否分得清武器和工具\N{\r英文}the difference between a weapon and a tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.96,1:07:16.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的语言如同文化般繁杂，有时一个词能表达两种意思\N{\r英文}Our language like a culture is messy, and sometimes one can be both.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.78,1:07:20.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他们很可能想说的是，让我们给他们东西\N{\r英文}I think it's quite possible that they are asking us to offer them something.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.39,1:07:22.16,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是反过来\N{\r英文}Not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.16,1:07:23.79,中文,,0,0,0,,就像贸易的雏形\N{\r英文}Like the first part of trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.79,1:07:27.10,中文,,0,0,0,,那除了这两个词，我们如何才能搞清他们的意图?\N{\r英文}So how do we clarify their intentions beyond those two words?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.10,1:07:30.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我再回去，我们立刻返回，找出真相\N{\r英文}I go back in.. right the way we go back in... we clear this out..
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.81,1:07:33.90,中文,,0,0,0,,- 实际操作要比那麻烦得多  - 哪麻烦了，你说说看？\N{\r英文}- It's more complicated than that.  - How is it more complicated than that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.84,1:07:38.04,中文,,0,0,0,,上校，国防部长要跟你通话\N{\r英文}Colonel, the Secretary of Defense is on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.34,1:07:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,在我们搞清这个之前，一定要保守秘密\N{\r英文}We need to sit on this information till we know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.83,1:07:52.41,中文,,0,0,0,,不能让我们的敌人知道了，我们还必须考虑一种可能性\N{\r英文}So we aren't sharing it with our enemies. We have to consider the idea
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.41,1:07:54.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的访客想以此来挑拨我们内斗\N{\r英文}that our visitors are prodding us to fight among ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.39,1:07:56.50,中文,,0,0,0,,直到仅有一方胜出\N{\r英文}untill only one faction prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.50,1:07:59.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你这么说根本没有依据  - 明显有\N{\r英文}- There is no evidence of that. - Sure there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.04,1:08:00.85,中文,,0,0,0,,随便翻开本史书\N{\r英文}Just grab a history book.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.27,1:08:04.23,中文,,0,0,0,,英国同印度，德国同卢旺达\N{\r英文}The British with India, the Germans with Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.96,1:08:07.34,中文,,0,0,0,,在匈牙利他们还专门造了个词\N{\r英文}They even got a name for it in Hungary.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.78,1:08:16.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我们生活在一个多极世界\N{\r英文}We are a world with no single leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.94,1:08:19.40,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能只挑选一国来打交道\N{\r英文}It's impossible to deal with just one of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.40,1:08:21.82,中文,,0,0,0,,现在又提到了武器\N{\r英文}With the word weapon now...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.82,1:08:23.59,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.68,1:08:50.27,中文,,0,0,0,,他们说了什么？\N{\r英文}What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.04,1:08:53.91,中文,,0,0,0,,中国和俄罗斯都离线了，还指望他们能说什么\N{\r英文}China and Russia are off the grid. They aren't speaking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.91,1:08:56.96,中文,,0,0,0,,不管他们在上一次对话中了解到什么，都被吓到了\N{\r英文}Whatever they learnt in the last session has them spooked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.39,1:09:01.15,中文,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\r英文}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.15,1:09:02.90,中文,,0,0,0,,命令我们也离线\N{\r英文}We have orders to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.90,1:09:06.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 等等，这些可是我们的盟友  - 上校，你不能这么做  - 关掉你的无线电\N{\r英文}- Wait these are our allies! - Colonel, you can't shut us down.  - Put your radio on silence!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.05,1:09:09.13,中文,,0,0,0,,- 照办  - 我们收到的消息是...\N{\r英文}- Do it.  - We received a message from the hep...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.83,1:09:11.42,中文,,0,0,0,,该死！\N{\r英文}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.76,1:09:14.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要保持对话\N{\r英文}We need to be talking to each other!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.38,1:09:16.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你想跟他们对话？先搞清这是什么意思\N{\r英文}You want to talk to them? Find out what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.23,1:09:26.34,中文,,0,0,0,,他们都下线了\N{\r英文}They are now offline...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.13,1:09:33.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们之前都没有重启过对话\N{\r英文}We've never re-entered the session before.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.56,1:09:36.22,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，相信我好吗？我们还来得及\N{\r英文}Louise, trust me ok? We got time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.22,1:09:38.15,中文,,0,0,0,,只需要加快进度，对吧？\N{\r英文}Just gotta step on it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.89,1:09:40.49,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}“使用武器”{\b}\N{\r英文}{\b1}"USE WEAPON"{\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.49,1:09:44.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是外星人发出的信息，促使中国政府在今天\N{\r英文}This is the alien message sent to provoke the Chinese government...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.08,1:09:48.09,中文,,0,0,0,,下令让他们的科学家退出国际合作任务\N{\r英文}to withdraw their scientists from the international mission today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.09,1:09:50.58,中文,,0,0,0,,在一份声明中，尚将军说道\N{\r英文}In a statement, General Shang said:
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.58,1:09:52.59,中文,,0,0,0,,对外星人的分化图谋\N{\r英文}"China no longer trusts the aliens
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.59,1:09:54.18,中文,,0,0,0,,中方表示遗憾\N{\r英文}who wants to divide us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.18,1:09:56.25,中文,,0,0,0,,会以保护全人类为己任\N{\r英文}Humanity must be protected. "
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.25,1:09:59.31,中文,,0,0,0,,中国请求联合国召开紧急会议\N{\r英文}China has asked for immediate talks at the UN.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.49,1:10:05.25,中文,,0,0,0,,A19，这是秃鹫，完毕\N{\r英文}Alpha 19, this is Condor. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.47,1:10:13.63,中文,,0,0,0,,A19，这是秃鹫，请讲，完毕\N{\r英文}Alpha 1-9, this is Condor. Come in. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.77,1:10:22.11,中文,,0,0,0,,马克斯上尉，这是秃鹫，没有收到回复\N{\r英文}Captain Marks, Condor, not receiving a transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.11,1:10:23.97,中文,,0,0,0,,收到的话，请回答\N{\r英文}Launch twice if you hear mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.91,1:10:29.26,中文,,0,0,0,,马克斯上尉，护送人员都被要求停止行动\N{\r英文}Captain Marks, all escorts are ordered to cease all activites...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.45,1:11:01.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不，不行，班克斯博士，你不能进去\N{\r英文}No, no, no... Dr. Banks, you can't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.71,1:11:04.42,中文,,0,0,0,,- 就让我问一个问题  - 班克斯博士\N{\r英文}- Just need to ask one question. - Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.80,1:11:08.07,中文,,0,0,0,,这次对话已经结束了，你不能再进去，会有危险的\N{\r英文}The session is finished. You can't go back in, it's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.07,1:11:10.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只需要5分钟，别拖走\N{\r英文}Look, we just need 5 minutes. Don't # it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.60,1:11:12.12,中文,,0,0,0,,莫里斯，放他们进去\N{\r英文}Morris, Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.57,1:11:16.32,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，阿波特\N{\r英文}Hey, Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.29,1:11:24.56,中文,,0,0,0,,那么，我们该如何称呼？第37次对话？\N{\r英文}So, what we are calling this? Session thirty-seven?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.01,1:11:28.60,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不，第36次对话第二段  - 好吧\N{\r英文}- No, thirty-six Part two.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.70,1:11:36.13,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么就你在这？\N{\r英文}Why are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.13,1:11:38.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直在试着联系马克斯上尉\N{\r英文}I've been attempting to hail Captain Marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.10,1:11:41.70,中文,,0,0,0,,- 护送小队不肯回应  - 为什么？\N{\r英文}- The escort unit are not responding.  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.31,1:11:43.71,中文,,0,0,0,,派出安保人员\N{\r英文}Send security.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.81,1:11:50.27,中文,,0,0,0,,给武器，问号\N{\r英文}Offer weapon... question mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.08,1:11:57.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你们要给我们什么吗？\N{\r英文}Are you offering us something?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.56,1:12:09.63,中文,,0,0,0,,技术，设备，方法\N{\r英文}Technology, apparatus, method...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.63,1:12:11.95,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，瞧见了吗？这是不同的词\N{\r英文}Yes, see this? This is a different word.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.95,1:12:15.02,中文,,0,0,0,,这个，这个弧线要臃肿得多\N{\r英文}This... this segment is a lot busier.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.86,1:12:23.51,中文,,0,0,0,,给   技术\N{\r英文}Give... technology...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.84,1:12:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\r英文}... Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.70,1:12:36.27,中文,,0,0,0,,他在做什么？\N{\r英文}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.92,1:12:44.53,中文,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\r英文}Captain. # check.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.91,1:12:55.03,中文,,0,0,0,,安保分队接近中，长官\N{\r英文}Security detail inbound, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.03,1:12:58.02,中文,,0,0,0,,4分钟后到达，我们会完成任务\N{\r英文}T-minus four minutes remaining. We need to see this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.42,1:13:00.27,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，都拿好武器，上膛\N{\r英文}OK, let's see, buckle and loads.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.27,1:13:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 坚决完成任务  - 明白\N{\r英文}- Which is pull this off until it's done. - Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.08,1:13:04.50,中文,,0,0,0,,他们开火的话，我们会还击\N{\r英文}We will shot if they use fire arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.50,1:13:08.03,中文,,0,0,0,,都上膛，找掩护，尽量避免伤亡\N{\r英文}Loads up and get under cover, stay, wo could avoid casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.82,1:13:37.28,中文,,0,0,0,,阿波特想让我去屏障那写\N{\r英文}Abbott wants me to write on the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.67,1:13:44.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你有这个本事？\N{\r英文}Can you even do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.37,1:13:46.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.96,1:14:05.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我用双手写不了\N{\r英文}I can't do it with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.29,1:15:17.87,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.55,1:15:34.98,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.12,1:16:22.81,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，别忙着起来\N{\r英文}Hey...Hey...Hey... Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.81,1:16:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你遭受了脑震荡，还是躺着吧\N{\r英文}You suffered a concussion. Just lay back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.58,1:16:30.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何？\N{\r英文}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.94,1:16:42.11,中文,,0,0,0,,- 伊恩怎么样了？  - 呃，和你一样，没什么大碍\N{\r英文}- How is Ian?  - Well, same as you. He is ok.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.90,1:16:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,- 谁......是谁干的？  - 几个小兵\N{\r英文}- Who... who did this?  - Some soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.47,1:16:50.59,中文,,0,0,0,,看电视看傻了\N{\r英文}Been watching too much TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.86,1:16:57.29,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么？  - 别紧张，别紧张\N{\r英文}- What is that?  - Take it easy... take it easy
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.30,1:17:01.26,中文,,0,0,0,,营地不再安全了，我们正等待疏散\N{\r英文}The site is not secure. We're on standby to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.26,1:17:02.92,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩呢？\N{\r英文}Where is Ian?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.54,1:17:06.25,中文,,0,0,0,,大约10分钟前，他们把他叫走了\N{\r英文}They probably got him maybe ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.57,1:17:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,得知你没事，他才肯离开的\N{\r英文}He wouldn't leave untill he knew you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.57,1:17:17.07,中文,,0,0,0,,帐篷里的人都在连轴转，想破解七肢桶给你的那个天书\N{\r英文}The whole tent is on the clock to figure out whatever it is you were given up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.02,1:17:24.58,中文,,0,0,0,,全都在这了？\N{\r英文}This is all of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.03,1:17:27.63,中文,,0,0,0,,图像信号没有因爆炸而中断？\N{\r英文}The feed wasn't interrupted by the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.27,1:17:30.19,中文,,0,0,0,,据我所知是这样\N{\r英文}As far as I can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.20,1:17:35.11,中文,,0,0,0,,- 有你能看懂的吗？  - 我还不知道\N{\r英文}- You see something?  - I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.43,1:17:38.40,中文,,0,0,0,,先得把我和路易丝的团队都召集起来\N{\r英文}I would need my team to get together with Louise's team.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.40,1:17:41.24,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这需要大家群策群力  - 我们还不能离开\N{\r英文}- I need everybody working on this.  - We can not leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.24,1:17:43.38,中文,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴你醒了  - 我们必须回去\N{\r英文}- Glad to see you awake.  - We need to go back in...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.38,1:17:45.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得向他们解释，这不是我们的过错\N{\r英文}We need to explain to them that this wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.47,1:17:47.43,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们不能再回去了  - 我们必须回去\N{\r英文}- We can't go back inside.  - We have to!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.82,1:17:49.73,中文,,0,0,0,,在那里面发生的是一起袭击\N{\r英文}What happened in there was an attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.73,1:17:52.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以指望最好的结果，可也要做好迎接报复的准备\N{\r英文}We can hope for the best, but we have to prepare for retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.61,1:17:54.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我们或许只能疏散\N{\r英文}We may have to evacuate...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.09,1:17:57.68,中文,,0,0,0,,那样做就错了，只要他们还停在那，我们就应该坚守\N{\r英文}That's a wrong move. As long as they stay, we have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.65,1:18:33.75,中文,,0,0,0,,他们并没飞走\N{\r英文}Well, they are not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.46,1:18:37.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么觉得要出大事？\N{\r英文}Why does it feel worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.24,1:18:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,中国摆出了进攻架势\N{\r英文}China is on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.01,1:18:47.82,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正调动军队，准备对外星人飞船发起攻击\N{\r英文}They are positioning their military to blow he alien vessel right out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.82,1:18:51.24,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦开战，我们不能坐以待毙\N{\r英文}If this happens, we can't sit and wait for their retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.44,1:18:53.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所以开始准备吧\N{\r英文}So get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.00,1:18:55.93,中文,,0,0,0,,空军和陆军正待命中\N{\r英文}The Air Force and Infantry are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.74,1:18:58.82,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}突发新闻{\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.82,1:19:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚，中国成为首个向外星人\N{\r英文}Tonight, China becomes the first world power
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.12,1:19:04.92,中文,,0,0,0,,宣战的世界大国\N{\r英文}To declare war against the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.92,1:19:08.49,中文,,0,0,0,,在联合国的外交斡旋宣告失败后\N{\r英文}Following the failure of the diplomatic efforts of the United Nations,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.49,1:19:11.81,中文,,0,0,0,,中国对外证实，他们的语言专家在今晚\N{\r英文}China has confirmed that its language experts had tonight...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.82,1:19:15.21,中文,,0,0,0,,向上海的外星人下达了最后通牒\N{\r英文}delivered an ultimatum at the Shanghai site.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.22,1:19:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,在一份电视声明中\N{\r英文}In a televised statement,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.62,1:19:19.48,中文,,0,0,0,,中国人民解放军最高统帅，尚将军\N{\r英文}Gen. Shang, chairman of the People's Liberation Army,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.48,1:19:23.38,中文,,0,0,0,,限令外星人24小时内撤出中国\N{\r英文}Said the aliens have twenty-four hours to leave Chinese territory,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.38,1:19:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不然将遭到毁灭性打击\N{\r英文}or face destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.16,1:19:26.95,中文,,0,0,0,,他还敦促其他国家的领导人\N{\r英文}And he urged all other world leaders
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.95,1:19:30.26,中文,,0,0,0,,与中国联合起来，采取一致行动\N{\r英文}to unite with China and take a similar stance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.95,1:19:34.38,中文,,0,0,0,,巴基斯坦，俄罗斯和苏丹都在本国的着陆点\N{\r英文}With a huge build up of forces at their landing sites,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.38,1:19:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,集结起大军\N{\r英文}Pakistan, Russia and Sudan
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.66,1:19:39.09,中文,,0,0,0,,预计会紧随中国采取行动\N{\r英文}Are thought to be following China's lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.79,1:19:56.75,中文,,0,0,0,,这肯定有章可循\N{\r英文}It can't be random.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.40,1:20:14.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我们怎么也得研究数年\N{\r英文}It's going to take us years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.56,1:20:21.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这里该用什么术语？\N{\r英文}What's this term here?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.03,1:20:26.65,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\r英文}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.09,1:20:31.41,中文,,0,0,0,,- 老妈？  - 嗯？\N{\r英文}- Mom?  - Hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.41,1:20:34.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝怎么了？  - 用来形容那个的术语\N{\r英文}- sweetie?  - What's this term for that thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.80,1:20:36.81,中文,,0,0,0,,像是科技术语\N{\r英文}Like a technical term...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.81,1:20:40.35,中文,,0,0,0,,就是我们达成协议，双方都有收获那种？\N{\r英文}Where we make a deal and we both get something out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.35,1:20:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,- 妥协吗？  - 不是\N{\r英文}- A compromise?  - No...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.92,1:20:46.32,中文,,0,0,0,,就好比竞争一样\N{\r英文}Like it's competition,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.32,1:20:48.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但结果都令双方满意\N{\r英文}But both sides end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.20,1:20:52.36,中文,,0,0,0,,是双赢吗？\N{\r英文}And win-win?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.36,1:20:54.43,中文,,0,0,0,,还要更有科学性\N{\r英文}more science-y than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.43,1:20:56.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你要问科学方面的，去打给你父亲\N{\r英文}If you want science, call your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.44,1:21:12.86,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.36,1:21:24.82,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\r英文}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.16,1:21:27.85,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\r英文}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.57,1:21:34.06,中文,,0,0,0,,现在什么时候了？\N{\r英文}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.51,1:21:38.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是你该拿出上等香槟庆祝的时候了\N{\r英文}It's time to open the bottle you've been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.10,1:21:44.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你有突破了，是吧？\N{\r英文}You cracked something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.62,1:21:46.80,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，快过来\N{\r英文}Yeah. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.53,1:21:51.88,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这部分，好像跟时间有关\N{\r英文}Take a look at this section. It seems to be talking about time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.88,1:21:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,他们表示“时间”的弧线无处不在\N{\r英文}Their segment for "time" is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.41,1:21:57.34,中文,,0,0,0,,这到底说的什么？\N{\r英文}So what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.98,1:22:00.71,中文,,0,0,0,,超光速旅行的方案吗？\N{\r英文}A formula for faster than light travel?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.34,1:22:02.85,中文,,0,0,0,,谁敢下结论？\N{\r英文}Who can tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.61,1:22:06.63,中文,,0,0,0,,中间缺了很多，并不完整\N{\r英文}It has too many gaps. It's not complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.63,1:22:08.05,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我恍然大悟\N{\r英文}Then it dawned on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.13,1:22:12.57,中文,,0,0,0,,就这儿\N{\r英文}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.63,1:22:16.38,中文,,0,0,0,,别盯着有字的区域，注意空白区域\N{\r英文}Stop focussing on the "one"s. Look at the "zero"s.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.55,1:22:20.15,中文,,0,0,0,,整个空间里面，有数据的区域和空白区域各占了多少？\N{\r英文}How much of it is data and how much of it is negative space?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.32,1:22:22.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我于是测了下\N{\r英文}So I measured it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.81,1:22:27.79,中文,,0,0,0,,两者之比是0.0833......\N{\r英文}0.0833 recurring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.96,1:22:35.18,中文,,0,0,0,,或许你想用分数来表达\N{\r英文}Perhaps you'd like to add that as a fraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.45,1:22:40.10,中文,,0,0,0,,十二分之一\N{\r英文}One of twelfth.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.00,1:22:46.83,中文,,0,0,0,,这里传达出的意思是，这只是十二块之一\N{\r英文}What is saying right here, is that, this is one of twelfth.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.93,1:22:48.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得到的只是全图的一块\N{\r英文}We are part of a larger whole.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.58,1:22:50.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这也有可能是让我们十二方厮杀的诱饵\N{\r英文}Or One of twelve contestants for the prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.68,1:22:52.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要向他汇报？\N{\r英文}Why do we have to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.23,1:22:53.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都是在这为国效命\N{\r英文}We all working together here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.43,1:22:55.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得联络其他着陆点\N{\r英文}We need to talk to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.65,1:22:57.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们应该主动支援，帮他们理解从其他七肢桶那得到的信息\N{\r英文}We need to help them with what they got from the other Heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.95,1:23:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你可别忘了，我们现在通讯管制了\N{\r英文}In case you don't remember, we're blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.20,1:23:02.93,中文,,0,0,0,,中国才威胁说要摧毁他们那的飞船，我们只能靠自己了\N{\r英文}China just threatened to destroy their Shell. We are on our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.93,1:23:04.80,中文,,0,0,0,,可这给的提示是所有分块能组合起来\N{\r英文}But it says that all the pieces fit together.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.80,1:23:06.99,中文,,0,0,0,,现在根本没人关心这些\N{\r英文}And I'm telling you that no one else cares.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.58,1:23:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,两小时前，我们从俄国的一个加密频道截取到一段音频\N{\r英文}Two hours ago we pulled this audio off a secured channel in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.96,1:23:13.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他们科学团队里的一名成员对外直播的\N{\r英文}Someone in their science team was broadcasting live.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.88,1:23:18.78,中文,,0,0,0,,在他们的最后一次对话中，外星人是这样说的\N{\r英文}In their final session, the alien said:
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.78,1:23:22.05,中文,,0,0,0,,时候到了，许多合而为一\N{\r英文}"There's no time. Many become one..."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.70,1:23:25.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们把武器都给完了\N{\r英文}I feel we have all the given weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.05,1:23:27.18,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有人收到这个的话\N{\r英文}If anyone is receiving this...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.71,1:23:29.37,中文,,0,0,0,,请......\N{\r英文}Please...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.49,1:23:36.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得......\N{\r英文}Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.16,1:23:39.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他刚刚说的话可以有各种解读\N{\r英文}There are a lot of ways you can interpret what he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.68,1:23:42.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不需要翻译来解读我也知道它的意思\N{\r英文}I don't need an interpreter to know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.08,1:23:45.60,中文,,0,0,0,,俄国为了保密，刚刚处决了自己的一名专家\N{\r英文}Russia just executed one of their own experts to keep their secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.60,1:23:47.81,中文,,0,0,0,,“许多合而为一”可能只是他们想表达\N{\r英文}"Many become one" could just be their way of saying
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.82,1:23:49.85,中文,,0,0,0,,“要进行一些组合”的意思\N{\r英文}Some assembly required.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.85,1:23:53.30,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么要分成块给我们？为什么不给我们完整的？\N{\r英文}Why hand it out to us in pieces? Why not give all over?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.30,1:23:56.04,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们人类破天荒的合作一次，没有比这更好的办法了吧？\N{\r英文}What better way to force us to work together for once?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.67,1:23:58.11,中文,,0,0,0,,就算我相信你\N{\r英文}Even if I did believe you,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.11,1:24:02.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你有天大的本事吗，能让其他国家乖乖配合，交出他们的数据？\N{\r英文}How in the world you can get anybody else to play along, and give out their data?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.84,1:24:04.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我们提供自己的来作交换\N{\r英文}We offer ours in return.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.95,1:24:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.01,1:24:10.05,中文,,0,0,0,,- 做交易吗？  - 这是非零和博弈\N{\r英文}- What, trade?  - It's a non-zero-sum game.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.79,1:24:14.61,中文,,0,0,0,,非零和博弈\N{\r英文}Non-zero-sum game.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.97,1:24:19.22,中文,,0,0,0,,就是它，太好了，谢谢\N{\r英文}That's it, yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.44,1:24:29.61,中文,,0,0,0,,有9个着陆点都实行了彻底的通讯管制\N{\r英文}Nine in the landing site are gone total com blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.18,1:24:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,要想联络他们，就只有开车去边境让他们的边防人员传话，我们已经在办了\N{\r英文}Only way to reach them is to physically drive there and yell at the border guards which we are doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.92,1:24:35.34,中文,,0,0,0,,可这样肯定来不及\N{\r英文}But it won't be fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.34,1:24:37.77,中文,,0,0,0,,一定有别的渠道来发消息\N{\r英文}There's gonna be a way to give the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.77,1:24:40.61,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们的盟友，可能有，不过到了这种局面，效果有限，也太迟了\N{\r英文}To our allies, maybe. But at this stage, it's too little, too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.62,1:24:44.01,中文,,0,0,0,,世界大战就要爆发了，我们却还联络不上各方\N{\r英文}What we need is to get all the other nations online...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.01,1:24:47.84,中文,,0,0,0,,当务之急是让有关各国都恢复联网\N{\r英文}before we start to go to war and there's no way for us to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.84,1:24:50.43,中文,,0,0,0,,等下，先等会儿，路易丝\N{\r英文}Wait. wait a second. Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.41,1:24:53.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们上方不就有渠道吗\N{\r英文}It's right above us.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.87,1:24:55.98,中文,,0,0,0,,可我们现在很难办到啊\N{\r英文}That's problematic for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.98,1:24:58.80,中文,,0,0,0,,五角大楼确信我们这的“蛋壳”会实施报复\N{\r英文}The Pentagon is convinced that our Shell will retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.80,1:25:01.55,中文,,0,0,0,,估计一个小时内就要下令疏散了\N{\r英文}My guess is order to evacuate within an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.66,1:25:06.07,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说，他们不是敌人，他们从未有过任何挑衅我们的行为\N{\r英文}Look, they are not our enemy. They made no act of aggression towards us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.07,1:25:08.15,中文,,0,0,0,,或许那就是他们的挑衅方式\N{\r英文}Maybe that's their way of being aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.15,1:25:11.26,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那不是问题所在  - 那问题是什么？\N{\r英文}- It's not the question. - Then what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.88,1:25:15.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我们如何能将你俩送回离地800米高的房间？\N{\r英文}How do we get you back in that room that's half a mile straight up?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.77,1:25:17.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得任务都结束了\N{\r英文}I think our work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.28,1:25:20.96,中文,,0,0,0,,现在交由我们的上级决断了\N{\r英文}It's in the hands of our superiors now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.60,1:25:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,她又想搞什么名堂？\N{\r英文}What the hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.12,1:29:01.84,中文,,0,0,0,,科斯特洛？\N{\r英文}Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.19,1:29:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,阿波特呢？\N{\r英文}Where is Abbott?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.91,1:29:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,“阿波特成了死的了”
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.52,1:29:36.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\r英文}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.18,1:29:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都很抱歉\N{\r英文}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.16,1:29:47.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你......\N{\r英文}I need you to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.23,1:29:51.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你发消息给其它着陆点\N{\r英文}I need you to send a message to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.99,1:30:01.31,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝有武器
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.28,1:30:10.94,中文,,0,0,0,,使用武器
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.94,1:30:14.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我不，我不明白\N{\r英文}I don't... I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.03,1:30:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你们来这的目的是什么？\N{\r英文}What is your purpose here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.12,1:30:28.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我们来帮助人类
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.76,1:30:36.67,中文,,0,0,0,,3000年后......
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.21,1:30:42.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要人类的帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.13,1:30:47.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能预知未来？\N{\r英文}How can you know the future?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.13,1:31:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我不......\N{\r英文}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.21,1:31:11.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白，这个孩子是谁？\N{\r英文}I don't understand. Who is this child?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.55,1:31:19.82,中文,,0,0,0,,这个节目的名字是“爸爸妈妈与动物交谈”\N{\r英文}The show is called "Mommy and Daddy talk to animals."
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.19,1:31:35.27,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝能预知未来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.99,1:31:48.73,中文,,0,0,0,,武器能打开时间之门
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.51,1:31:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,等下...... 别走，等下！\N{\r英文}Wait... No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.61,1:32:48.01,中文,,0,0,0,,- 班克斯博士！  - 路易丝！\N{\r英文}- Dr. Banks!  - Louise!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.01,1:32:49.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.73,1:32:54.84,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？  - 嗯\N{\r英文}- You all right?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.84,1:32:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,过来吧，发生了什么？\N{\r英文}Come here. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.57,1:32:58.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我正想搞明白，这事关重大\N{\r英文}I tried to figure it out, this is too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.37,1:33:00.94,中文,,0,0,0,,现在都不重要了，我们接到命令要疏散了\N{\r英文}It doesn't matter now. We have orders to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.11,1:33:04.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？  - 俄国和苏丹会效仿中国\N{\r英文}- Why?  - Russia and Sudan will follow China.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.01,1:33:09.26,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，我不明白这是为什么\N{\r英文}Ian... I do not understand why...?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.26,1:33:11.26,中文,,0,0,0,,帮帮我，妈妈\N{\r英文}Help me, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.26,1:33:12.92,中文,,0,0,0,,路易斯\N{\r英文}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.75,1:33:15.21,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈！\N{\r英文}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.36,1:33:18.92,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈!\N{\r英文}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.35,1:33:23.30,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，宝贝\N{\r英文}Sorry, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.45,1:33:28.75,中文,,0,0,0,,今天星期几，宝贝你知道吗？\N{\r英文}What day is it, do you know baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.75,1:33:30.30,中文,,0,0,0,,星期天\N{\r英文}Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.79,1:33:38.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你要像爸爸那样离开我吗？\N{\r英文}Are you gonna leave me like Daddy did?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.75,1:33:41.99,中文,,0,0,0,,哎，汉娜宝贝，你爸爸没有离开你\N{\r英文}Oh, Hannah, honey, your daddy didn't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.83,1:33:45.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你会见到他的，就这个周末\N{\r英文}You're gonna see him... this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.16,1:33:48.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他看我的眼神和以前不同了\N{\r英文}He never look me the same way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.22,1:33:59.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这要怪我\N{\r英文}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.13,1:34:04.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟他说了些事，他一时半会儿没法接受\N{\r英文}I told him something that he wasn't ready to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.21,1:34:07.89,中文,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.55,1:34:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,呃......\N{\r英文}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.63,1:34:13.55,中文,,0,0,0,,信不信由你\N{\r英文}Believe it or not...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.00,1:34:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道将来会发生的事\N{\r英文}I know something that's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.86,1:34:21.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我也没法解释清楚，我就是知道\N{\r英文}I can not explain how I know it, I just do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.03,1:34:26.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在我告诉你爸爸后，他气坏了\N{\r英文}And when I told your daddy, he got really mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.12,1:34:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他说我做了错误的选择\N{\r英文}He said I made the wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.06,1:34:36.08,中文,,0,0,0,,将来会发生什么？\N{\r英文}What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.91,1:34:41.01,中文,,0,0,0,,会发生的事和\N{\r英文}It has to do with a...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.01,1:34:42.76,中文,,0,0,0,,一种罕见的疾病有关\N{\r英文}A very rare disease.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.77,1:34:47.90,中文,,0,0,0,,并且这种病是势不可挡的\N{\r英文}And it's unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.73,1:34:51.77,中文,,0,0,0,,有点像你一样\N{\r英文}Kind of like you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.33,1:34:53.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你是如此神奇\N{\r英文}You're so amazing
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.73,1:34:58.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你的诗歌，还有你给世界献上的各种美妙事物\N{\r英文}And your poetry and all the other amazing things that you share with the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.35,1:35:03.59,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我势不可挡？  - 嗯\N{\r英文}- I'm unstoppable?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.49,1:35:22.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我扶着你\N{\r英文}I got you...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.51,1:35:25.01,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.61,1:35:27.11,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.64,1:35:31.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚得知丈夫为何离开我\N{\r英文}I just realized why my husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.19,1:35:32.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫离开了我\N{\r英文}My husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.04,1:35:34.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你已经结婚了？\N{\r英文}You have been married?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.73,1:35:37.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我们赶紧走吧\N{\r英文}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.13,1:36:14.02,中文,,0,0,0,,- 妈妈  - 嗯？\N{\r英文}- Mama.  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.76,1:36:16.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我的名字为什么叫“汉娜”\N{\r英文}Why my name is Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.23,1:36:25.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你的名字很特别\N{\r英文}Your name is very special.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.09,1:36:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,因为它是回文\N{\r英文}Because it is a palindrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.28,1:36:30.87,中文,,0,0,0,,顺读倒读均相同的字\N{\r英文}It reads the same word from backwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.31,1:36:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,- 关了它  - 把它放到那里\N{\r英文}- Turn it off.  - That goes back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.84,1:36:57.93,中文,,0,0,0,,宇宙文
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.64,1:37:07.64,中文,,0,0,0,,赠与汉娜
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.84,1:37:09.08,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\r英文}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.08,1:37:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\r英文}We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.43,1:37:13.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我们把它带走就是了\N{\r英文}Let's take this with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.94,1:37:19.91,中文,,0,0,0,,宇宙文 — 著者：路易丝
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.91,1:37:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,七文翻译指南
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.63,1:37:39.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我看得懂\N{\r英文}I can read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.29,1:37:44.94,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我知道它的意思  - 你说什么?\N{\r英文}- I know what it is.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.94,1:37:47.57,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是什么武器，这是件礼物\N{\r英文}It's not a weapon. It's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.05,1:37:49.99,中文,,0,0,0,,武器是指他们的语言\N{\r英文}The weapon is their language.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.99,1:37:52.34,中文,,0,0,0,,他们全都交给了我们，你明不明白？\N{\r英文}They gave it all to us. Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.34,1:37:54.78,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们能学会他们的语言？\N{\r英文}So we can learn Heptopods?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.78,1:37:57.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你去学习的话，并且当你真正精通后\N{\r英文}If you learn it... when you really learn it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.86,1:38:00.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你就会用他们的方式感知时间\N{\r英文}You begin to perceive time the way they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.56,1:38:03.18,中文,,0,0,0,,这，这样你就能知道将来会发生什么\N{\r英文}So, so you can see what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.18,1:38:06.01,中文,,0,0,0,,而且，他们所理解的时间和我们并不相同\N{\r英文}But time, it isn't the same for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.01,1:38:08.26,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是非线性的  - 听着\N{\r英文}- It is not linear.  - Look...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.27,1:38:10.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我们竭尽所能了，可还是差一点\N{\r英文}We did our best, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.62,1:38:15.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你们跟这位上尉走，5分钟后起飞\N{\r英文}The captain, you'll lift off in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.44,1:38:19.23,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，路易丝，跟你们共事是我的荣幸\N{\r英文}Ian, Louise. It was an honor to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.94,1:38:21.55,中文,,0,0,0,,一路顺风\N{\r英文}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.72,1:38:26.40,中文,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\r英文}Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.08,1:38:34.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我去问下我们的目的地\N{\r英文}I'll find out where we are going.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.22,1:38:45.33,中文,,0,0,0,,醒醒，妈妈\N{\r英文}Wake up, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.75,1:39:22.50,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.48,1:39:24.94,中文,,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\r英文}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.27,1:39:28.66,中文,,0,0,0,,尚将军，是我很荣幸才对\N{\r英文}General Shang, the pleasure is mine, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.17,1:39:30.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你们的总统说\N{\r英文}Your president said...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.31,1:39:34.59,中文,,0,0,0,,能邀请我参加这个宴会是很荣幸的事\N{\r英文}It was an honor to host me in the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.59,1:39:36.91,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是啊  - 可我要坦白\N{\r英文}- Yes.  - But I confess...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.37,1:39:40.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我出席的唯一原因是\N{\r英文}The only reason why I am here is...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.56,1:39:43.39,中文,,0,0,0,,想亲自见你一面\N{\r英文}To meet you in person.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.42,1:39:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我真是受宠若惊，谢谢你\N{\r英文}Well, Im flattered. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.94,1:39:52.35,中文,,0,0,0,,18个月前，你做了件了不起的事\N{\r英文}Eighteen months ago, you did something remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.10,1:39:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,连我上司都没这个本事\N{\r英文}Something not even my superior has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.44,1:40:01.94,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是什么事？  - 你改变了我的心意\N{\r英文}- What's that?  - You changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.94,1:40:08.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你是我们能联合起来的原因\N{\r英文}You are the reason for this unification.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.67,1:40:12.32,中文,,0,0,0,,多亏你拨通了我的私人号码\N{\r英文}All because you reached out to me on my private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.78,1:40:18.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你的私人号码？将军，我并不知道啊\N{\r英文}Your private number? General I do not know your private number...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.53,1:40:27.15,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了\N{\r英文}Now you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.39,1:40:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我不敢宣称自己知道你是怎么想的，不过\N{\r英文}I do not claim to know how your mind works, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.54,1:40:37.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信你必须得看到我的号码\N{\r英文}I believe it was important for you to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.61,1:40:40.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我的确打了你的电话，对吧？\N{\r英文}I called you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.41,1:40:42.99,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，你打了\N{\r英文}Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.18,1:40:56.69,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.48,1:41:14.85,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，都关机吧\N{\r英文}All right, let's shut down the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.85,1:41:18.85,中文,,0,0,0,,长官，这里有部卫星电话正打给中国\N{\r英文}Sir... there's a satelite here dialling China.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.19,1:41:22.78,中文,,0,0,0,,这里？你什么意思？\N{\r英文}Here? What do you mean here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.06,1:41:26.87,中文,,0,0,0,,快接啊\N{\r英文}Come on, answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.88,1:41:29.50,中文,,0,0,0,,那是谁的电话？\N{\r英文}Whose phone is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.65,1:41:35.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是你的电话，长官\N{\r英文}It's your phone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.19,1:41:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,搜索营地，马上去办\N{\r英文}Search base camp now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.16,1:41:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,给我找出用电话的人\N{\r英文}Find out who is using that phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.25,1:41:48.91,中文,,0,0,0,,- 盯着它的位置  - 遵命\N{\r英文}- Hold on to those co-ordinates.  - Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.91,1:41:51.79,中文,,0,0,0,,快接，我该说什么？\N{\r英文}C'mon... What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.27,1:41:54.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我该说什么？\N{\r英文}What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.12,1:42:10.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我说的话，我会永生难忘\N{\r英文}I would never forget what you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.56,1:42:23.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我说了我妻子的临终遗言\N{\r英文}You told me my wife's dying words.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.43,1:42:42.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们找到电话源头了\N{\r英文}We found the source of the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.97,1:42:45.23,中文,,0,0,0,,就在清理间，等候指示\N{\r英文}It is in the clean room. Waiting for the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.77,1:42:48.79,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，你在做什么？\N{\r英文}Louise... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.87,1:42:52.13,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你在做什么？  - 让尚将军改变心意\N{\r英文}- What are you doing?  - Changing shang's mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.14,1:42:53.54,中文,,0,0,0,,帮我争取20秒钟\N{\r英文}You buy me twenty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.54,1:42:55.24,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们来不及了  - 来得及，相信我\N{\r英文}- We do not have time.  - No. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.24,1:42:58.18,中文,,0,0,0,,- 帮我争取20秒，你相信我吗？  - 好吧\N{\r英文}- Buy me twenty seconds. Do you trust me?  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.09,1:43:02.88,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.89,1:43:04.86,中文,,0,0,0,,马上放下电话，不然我们要开枪了\N{\r英文}Drop the phone now, or we shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.80,1:43:10.39,中文,,0,0,0,,- 放下！  - 我很抱歉\N{\r英文}- Drop it!  - I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.90,1:43:14.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在的行为是在叛国！\N{\r英文}You're committing an act of treason!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.08,1:43:22.85,中文,,0,0,0,,- 放下  - 打完了\N{\r英文}- Drop it!  - It's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.85,1:43:24.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我打完了\N{\r英文}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.67,1:43:41.87,中文,,0,0,0,,12个着陆点的通讯管制\N{\r英文}The communications blackout from all twelve landing sites...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.87,1:43:44.20,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚仍在持续\N{\r英文}continues this evening...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.20,1:43:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,- 可能性......等下，我们刚收到消息  - 两个问题是......\N{\r英文}- The possibility of... Hold on... We are just hearing...  - The two questiones...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.62,1:43:50.18,中文,,0,0,0,,- 现在我们要中断这则报道，插播突发新闻  - 刚收到的突发新闻\N{\r英文}- I'm being told we're going to cut this report to tell you breaking news.  - This news just in, breaking now...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.18,1:43:52.47,中文,,0,0,0,,中国突然召开了一场新闻发布会\N{\r英文}China has called an emergency press conference...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.48,1:43:55.78,中文,,0,0,0,,中国人民解放军总司令，尚将军\N{\r英文}General Shang, Commanding Chief of the People's Liberation Army...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.78,1:43:59.98,中文,,0,0,0,,在新闻发布会上宣布，中国会立即撤军\N{\r英文}has announced in an emergency press conference that China is standing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.98,1:44:02.90,中文,,0,0,0,,中国宣布，他们收集到的所有情报\N{\r英文}China is stating that all the intelligence they have received...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.91,1:44:05.60,中文,,0,0,0,,将会立即和其他着陆点分享\N{\r英文}will be shared immediately with all the other landing site...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.88,1:44:08.38,中文,,0,0,0,,世界各地的科学家正认真审查来自英国、日本、塞拉利昂等国的信息\N{\r英文}Sientists from around the world are sifting through the information recieved from UK, Japan, Sierra Leone...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.38,1:44:11.17,中文,,0,0,0,,突发新闻，俄罗斯军队现在公开了\N{\r英文}Breaking news, the Russian arm forces are now revealing...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.17,1:44:15.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他们从自己两个着落点收集到的信息，并宣布黑海为非军事区\N{\r英文}the information they acquired from both their landing sites, had declared the black sea a demilitarized zone...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.30,1:44:19.05,中文,,0,0,0,,谜题的十二个分块正被慢慢的拼到一起\N{\r英文}...the twelve pieces of this puzzle that is being slowly put together.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.43,1:46:11.73,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，汉娜\N{\r英文}So, Hannah...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.52,1:46:15.01,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你故事的源头\N{\r英文}This is where your story begins.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.12,1:46:19.19,中文,,0,0,0,,他们离去的那天\N{\r英文}The day they departed.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.18,1:46:24.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.95,1:46:30.45,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管已提前知晓人生\N{\r英文}Despite knowing the journey...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.76,1:46:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,以及它的走向\N{\r英文}and where it leads...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.41,1:46:37.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我无所畏惧\N{\r英文}I embrace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.59,1:46:42.86,中文,,0,0,0,,并且会珍惜每一分钟\N{\r英文}And I welcome every moment of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.61,1:47:02.30,中文,,0,0,0,,H-A-N 汉， N-A-H 娜\N{\r英文}H-A-N-N-A-H.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.01,1:47:17.87,中文,,0,0,0,,现在反过来念\N{\r英文}Now backwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.87,1:47:21.39,中文,,0,0,0,,H-A-N 汉， N-A-H 娜\N{\r英文}H-A-N-N-A-H.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.39,1:47:22.90,中文,,0,0,0,,汉娜\N{\r英文}Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.90,1:47:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了，宝贝？\N{\r英文}You ready, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.48,1:47:29.35,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了  - 嘿\N{\r英文}- OK.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.00,1:47:32.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了吗？  - 好了，你去吧\N{\r英文}- It's okay?  - Yes, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.11,1:47:36.81,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\r英文}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.95,1:47:49.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？  - 让爸爸从你身上翻过去\N{\r英文}- Are you ok?  - Daddy just roll over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.59,1:47:53.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？\N{\r英文}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.54,1:47:59.43,中文,,0,0,0,,今天讲星星的故事哦\N{\r英文}Guess what... star stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.56,1:48:03.85,中文,,0,0,0,,- 伊恩  - 嗯\N{\r英文}- Ian.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.58,1:48:07.84,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你能一览自己的人生，从出生到死亡\N{\r英文}If you could see your whole life, from start to finish...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.95,1:48:12.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你会尝试改变吗？\N{\r英文}Would you change things?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.07,1:48:19.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我或许......\N{\r英文}Maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.31,1:48:23.41,中文,,0,0,0,,会尽量多吐露心声，天晓得呢\N{\r英文}I say what I feel more often. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.28,1:48:41.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗，从我能记事起，我就总是\N{\r英文}You know, I've had my head tilted up to the stars
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.63,1:48:43.80,中文,,0,0,0,,对天上的星星着迷\N{\r英文}for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.97,1:48:48.38,中文,,0,0,0,,可你知道什么让我最惊喜吗？\N{\r英文}But you know what surprised me the most?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.33,1:48:52.28,中文,,0,0,0,,并不是遇见他们\N{\r英文}It was not meeting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.26,1:48:58.95,中文,,0,0,0,,而是遇见你\N{\r英文}It was meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.51,1:49:42.60,中文,,0,0,0,,被你抱着的感觉还是如此温暖啊\N{\r英文}I'd forgotten how good it felt to be held by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.35,1:49:54.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你想生个宝宝吗？\N{\r英文}Do you want to make a baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.51,1:50:32.09,中文,,0,0,0,,想，想啊\N{\r英文}Yes... yeah!
